{"_id":"07DgmrhScaPwGUwr","name":"黑曜燧石龙板甲 Obsidian Flint Dragon Plate","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-banded-steel-studded.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>着装这副护甲时，你的AC获得+2加值并且获得对毒素伤害的抗性。此外，你在对抗或结束擒抱状态的属性检定和豁免检定中获得优势。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":65,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":20,"type":"heavy","dex":0},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"plate","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":15,"stealth":true,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[{"_id":"Z0TGPeq6zaDtSB3T","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.di.value","mode":2,"value":"poison"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-banded-steel-studded.webp","label":"+ 毒素抗性","origin":"Item.07DgmrhScaPwGUwr","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1lJWhHNIfAVjHQ0W","name":"灵能水晶 Psi Crystal","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-cluster-pink.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需智力为3或更高的生物同调）</em></p>\n<p>只要你仍与该水晶同调，你得到心灵感应Telepathy能力。关于该能力的相关规则，请查阅怪物图鉴中的介绍。当你与它同调时，该水晶还会与你的内心相感应，从而散发出紫色的心灵之光。你的智力越高，它所能产生的光芒就越强烈，心灵感应的范围也就越大（见下表）。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\">灵能水晶效应表</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><strong> 智力</strong></th>\n<th><strong>心灵感应范围</strong></th>\n<th><strong>照明强度</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>3~7</td>\n<td>15尺</td>\n<td>5尺微光光照</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8~11</td>\n<td>30尺</td>\n<td>5尺明亮光照以及其外5尺微光光照</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>12~15</td>\n<td>60尺</td>\n<td>0尺明亮光照以及其外10尺微光光照</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>16+</td>\n<td>120尺</td>\n<td>5尺明亮光照以及其外15尺微光光照</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"IDRotF","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1rBzDwKjEMYBbWyD","name":"蔚蓝之锋 Azuredge","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-double-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>(需同调)</em></p>\n<p>这把智能战斧由大法师阿格哈荣 Ahghairon 铸造用以守护深水城。它目前的持有者是前灰色小队成员梅伦·战龙 Meloon Wardragon，但它正在寻求一名新主人。</p>\n<p>蔚蓝之锋的钢制斧柄上刻着细小的符文，并以蓝龙皮包覆，头部镶嵌着一颗星光蓝宝石。散发着深蓝色微光的斧头则以银、银金和钢合金制成。</p>\n<p>你在使用此魔法武器进行的攻击和伤害骰上获得+3 加值。另外，这把武器可以穿过护盾术产生的魔法屏障， 无视其提供的防护。</p>\n<p>当你使用这把战斧命中邪魔或不死生物时，斧刃上爆发出的冰蓝色火焰会对目标造成额外 2d6 光耀伤害。</p>\n<p><strong>投掷。</strong>这把战斧有 3 发充能。你可以消耗 1 发充能， 将此斧视为具有投掷属性，射程 60/180 英尺的武器，并 用它进行一次远程攻击。无论命中与否，此斧会在当前回合结束时飞回你身边、落在你手中或是你脚边(由你决定)。 此斧每天黎明时恢复全部已消耗的充能。</p>\n<p><strong>照明。</strong>持握此斧时，你可以用一个动作让它发出蓝光或熄灭。这种蓝光可以提供 30 英尺半径的明亮光照以及该范围外 30 英尺的微光光照。</p>\n<p><strong>智能。</strong>蔚蓝之锋是一把守序中立的智能武器，其属性值为智力 12、感知 15、魅力 15。它拥有听觉和 150 英尺的黑暗视觉。</p>\n<p>蔚蓝之锋可以说、读、理解通用语并且能用心灵感应和持用者交流。它的声音冷静而温和。另外，它能感知到 120 英尺范围内任何非守序生物的存在。</p>\n<p><strong>性格。</strong>蔚蓝之锋誓言守护深水城，因此它希望自己的主人是一名遵纪守法的，愿意为了保护深水城奉献出自己一切的人。它非常耐心，不吝惜在寻找理想主人这件事上多花时间。</p>\n<p>如果有人试图违背蔚蓝之锋的意愿使用它，它可能会 让自己的重量变为通常的十倍，也可能会靠魔力吸附到它接触到的任何中型或更大的物体或表面上。这样一来就没人能挥舞它了。若想将蔚蓝之锋从它吸附的物体或表面上取下，只能摧毁两者之一，或是使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xjn6gjItpWpldE53]{祈愿术 Wish}。当然，它自己可以随时决定终止效果。</p>\n<p><em>注：需要的话，其他公式已设为骰命中邪魔或不死生物时的光耀伤害。</em></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDH","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"3","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"3","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+@mod+3","slashing"]],"versatile":"1d10+@mod+3"},"formula":"2d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"battleaxe","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":true,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"mgc":true,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2iANFecAP6agjBUV","name":"黑杖 Blackstaff","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/wands/wand-carved-stone-shard.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>法杖(需黑杖继承人同调，必须为法师)</em></p>\n<p>黑杖是一把智能法杖，上面雕刻着符文并以银色纹理 装饰。它是深水城至高法师“黑杖”的职位象征。作为黑 杖的合法拥有者，瓦婕拉·萨法尔是唯一能与黑杖同调的 人。然而，黑杖可以自行选择一名新主人(见下文“性格”)。</p>\n<p>黑杖具有@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.2D7CD67D4B76A599]{威力法杖 Staff of Power}的属性，以及下列额外属性。</p>\n<p><strong>活化自走巨像。</strong>你可以用一个动作并消耗 1 发或更多 充能激活或关停深水城的一尊或多尊自走巨像 walking statues，每激活或关停一尊雕像消耗 1 发充 能。你只能在深水城中使用该能力。被活化的巨像遵从被困在法杖中的凯尔本·奥罗桑 Khelben Arunsun 的精神指令(见下文“性格”)。当黑杖被摧毁或巨像自身被关停 时，自走巨像将变回普通雕像。</p>\n<p><strong>解除魔法。</strong>你可以用一个附赠动作并消耗 1 发充能以施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.as6xgBANCbyoWPXX]{解除魔法 Dispel Magic}，目标为你用法杖尖端碰触的 一名生物、一件物品或一个魔法效果。如果目标是一名非自愿生物或是一件由非自愿生物持有的物品，你必须先用黑杖进行一次近战攻击并命中该生物，之后才能消耗充能施放解除魔法。</p>\n<p><strong>魔力耗竭。</strong>此属性只影响有法术位的生物。当你在近战攻击中用黑杖命中一名有法术位的生物时，你可以用一 个附赠动作并消耗 1 发充能令该生物损失一个他能施放的 最高环法术的法术位。如果该生物已经用尽了所有法术位， 那么就不会受到任何影响。该生物在进行长休之后可以如常恢复因此效果损失的法术位。</p>\n<p><strong>附魔大师。</strong>当你持握黑杖施放一个 1 环或更高的附魔 学派法术时，你可以进行一次智力(奥秘)检定，DC 为 10+法术环阶。如果检定成功，则你此次施法无需消耗法术位。</p>\n<p><strong>智能。</strong>黑杖是一把绝对中立的智能法杖，其属性值为 智力 22、感知 15、魅力 18。它拥有听觉和 120 英尺的黑 暗视觉，并能用心灵感应和握持它的任何生物交流。</p>\n<p><strong>性格。</strong>这把法杖里囚禁了历任黑杖的灵魂。它的创造者凯尔本·奥罗桑 Khelben Arunsun 是所有灵魂中占支配地位的一个。黑杖像凯尔本本人一样，极度狡诈，并且喜 欢操纵别人。它偏好给主人提出建议而非直接影响他。这 把法杖的主要目标是保护深水城和深水城公开领主(目前 是莱拉·银手)，次要目的是帮助其持用者变得更强。<br />如果它的主人不再按它的意愿行事，黑杖将关闭自己 的能力，直至找到一位对深水城无比忠诚的合格继承者。</p>\n<p><strong>灵魂陷阱。</strong>当一名黑杖死去时，他的灵魂将与历任黑杖一起被囚禁在法杖中。他也因此无法被复活。<br />摧毁黑杖将释放其中囚禁的所有灵魂，但凯尔本的灵 魂可以寄宿到法杖的任意一块碎片上。这块碎片会保留黑 杖的智能属性，但失去其他所有属性。只要这块碎片还存 在，凯尔本的灵魂就能在任何时候将黑杖重组。法杖重组 后，历任黑杖的灵魂将继续被囚禁于其中。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDH","quantity":1,"weight":4,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":20,"max":"20","per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"2","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6+@mod+2","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":"1d8+@mod+2"},"formula":"2d8+4","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"quarterstaff","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":true,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"mgc":true,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2j0HhhMefRDL77i9","name":"巨龙符文之爪 Claw of the Wyrm Rune","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/claws/claw-lizard-white-black.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这枚龙爪上覆盖着一层银铸的外衣，上面雕刻着wyrm（龙）的符文。该爪具有以下特性。</p>\n<p><strong>屠龙者Wyrmslayer</strong>。以一个动作，你可以以该爪指向一个距你30尺以内的龙。该龙必须通过一个DC15的体质豁免，否则对所有类型的伤害获得易伤，直到你的下一回合结束。此特性可以使用三次。在下一次黎明时，该爪恢复所有消耗的次数。</p>\n<p><strong>防龙盾Wyrm Shield</strong>。当该爪被装饰在你的身上时，你对龙的吐息所造成的伤害具有抗性。</p>\n<p><strong>隔离龙族Wyrm Ward</strong>。通过用你的手指在地面描绘wyrm符文，你可以将爪的魔法转移到某一地方。由你所描绘的那个点成为一个半径100尺的球形魔法区域的中心，该区域的位置是固定的。转移该项魔力需要花费8小时时间，并且需要爪在这期间一直位于你的5尺之内。在这8小时结束时，爪被摧毁，该区域获得以下特性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>当位于此100尺半径的球形范围内时，任何龙类在豁免骰上具有劣势，并且其飞行速度不可超过10尺。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SKT","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"3","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"30zHkjP6GD7bybcl","name":"地狱火长柄刀 Hellfire Glaive","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/glaive.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":6,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d10 + @mod","slashing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"glaive","properties":{"hvy":true,"two":true,"rch":true,"amm":false,"ver":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"mgc":true,"lgt":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3A3vDIxJLbXnEUkc","name":"地狱火骑枪 Hellfire Lance","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/arrow_02.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":6,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d12 + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"lance","properties":{"amm":false,"hvy":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"rch":true,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":true,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false,"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3AnGVAzdDGYbjGj0","name":"抗火魔斗篷 Piwafwi of Fire Resistance","type":"equipment","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/equipment/cloak-fur.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<h4><strong>卓尔制品Drowcraft Items </strong></h4>\n<p>由卓尔制作的（或是由幽暗地域其他种族制作的某些）魔法物品，都是由一些无法接触日光的物质或仪式制成。许多这类物品（包括卓尔的护甲、武器和魔法斗篷之类）当暴露在阳光下超过1小时就会失去其魔力。充能物品则会被彻底摧毁。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这是一件@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.34F1570579A78365]{精灵斗篷 Cloak of Elvenkind}。它同时还能使其着装者额外获得火焰伤害抗性。该斗篷在阳光下连续暴露超过1 个小时将会魔力尽失。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"OoTA","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"拉起兜帽。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"clothing","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3J6Sbk4JGJ2jmb9O","name":"碎棘 Shatterspike","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/greatsword-crossguard-steel.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>你用该魔法武器发动的攻击检定和伤害掷骰具+1 加值。以其命中物件时将直接造成重击，且可以选择对该物件造成钝击或挥砍伤害（由你选择）。此外，非魔法来源的伤害无法损伤该武器。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TftYP","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"+1","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+1+@mod","slashing"]],"versatile":"1d10+1+@mod"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"longsword","properties":{"ver":true,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":true,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3RQSSkF83Sdz89g6","name":"集雨器 Rain Catcher","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/leather/leather-scraps-yellow.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>集雨器是一种简易装置，由一块 5 尺见方的防水皮革和一个带 腿的木制框架组成。当防水皮革铺在木框上时，它下凹形成一 个水盆，每寸降雨量可以生成 2 加仑饮用水，最多可容纳 8 加仑。防水皮革和木制框架可折叠，便于运输。一个集雨器售价1 gp，重5磅。</p>\n<p>南扎路港的集雨器销售由贸易亲王艾珂内·阿法垄断。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":5,"price":1,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"49HnrlgFqmKirDBa","name":"太阳剑 Sunsword","type":"weapon","img":"icons/magic/fire/beam-jet-stream-trails-orange.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>太阳剑是一把世间罕有的宝剑，曾经属于施特拉德的兄弟谢尔盖·冯·扎洛维奇。它原本有铂金的剑柄和护手以及坚如钢铁的锋利水晶剑刃。</p>\n<p>在谢尔盖死后，施特拉德雇佣了一个名叫卡赞的强大法师来销毁这把武器。其过程的第一步是要把剑柄与剑刃分开——卡赞完成了这个部分。但在卡赞摧毁剑刃的时候，他的学徒却偷走了剑柄和护手。卡赞后来把这名学徒支离破碎的尸体丢进了斯瓦里奇森林，但他在哪都找不到剑柄。为了避免吸血鬼发怒，卡赞告诉施特拉德整把剑都已经被摧毁了。</p>\n<p>这把剑柄有自己的智能，它明白自己已经永远不可能再和原来的水晶剑刃合二为一。然而，它却得到了@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.152FDAA04D28AF9E]{阳炎剑 Sun Blade}的属性。</p>\n<p><strong>智能Sentience</strong>。太阳剑是一把有智能的，混乱善良的武器，具有 11 点智力，17 点感知，16 点魅力。它的听觉范围是 60 尺，也具有 60 尺的普通视觉。该武器通过传递情绪来和携带或使用它的生物交流。</p>\n<p><strong>个性Personality</strong>。太阳剑的特别想要摧毁施特拉德，这并不是因为它很想解放巴洛维亚，而是因为它想要报复令它失去水晶剑刃的人。这把剑在背地里十分担心自己被摧毁。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CoS","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"2","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8 + @mod +2","radiant"]],"versatile":"1d10 + @mod +2"},"formula":"1d8","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"longsword","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":true,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":true,"mgc":true,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4BH8XuZqPrdMptxn","name":"心灵控制药水（人类）Potion of Mind Control (humanoid)","type":"consumable","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-conical-corked-purple.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>饮用心灵控制药水后，你可以在自己下个回合结束前对某一指定生物施展支配法术（豁免DC 15）。如果你不施展该法术，则该药水的效应将浪费掉。</p>\n<p>心灵控制药水（人类）能产生@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.JudswpO6E5GBlyfQ]{支配人类 Dominate Person（类人生物humanoid）}。如果目标的首次豁免失败，其效应将持续 1 小时，且你无须保持专注。在效应持续期间，被魅惑生物再次进行破除该效应的豁免检定时都将承受劣势。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TftYP","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"abil","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"potion","attuned":false,"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4FzumRdBOvI6eFsv","name":"反噬之标枪 Javelin of Backbiting","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/spear-flared-wrapped.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>你用该魔法武器发动的攻击检定和伤害掷骰具 +2 加值。用其进行投掷时，它的常规和最大射程都增加 30 尺，且命中后增加一枚额外的伤害骰。投掷完成后，它无论是否命中都会立即飞回你手中。</p>\n<p><strong>诅咒Curse</strong>。与这支受诅咒武器同调的生物将受到其诅咒影响。只要诅咒还在生效，你总是会把它放在触手可及的地方，不愿与它分开。此外，你使用除它之外的任何武器发动攻击检定时具有劣势。</p>\n<p>以该武器发动攻击检定骰出 1 时，它会突然弯曲或飞转攻击你的后背。进行一次带优势的攻击检定，对抗你自身AC。若命中，则你受到伤害，如同你用它捅了自己。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TftYP","quantity":1,"weight":2,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":60,"long":150,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"+2","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6+2+@mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"javelin","properties":{"thr":true,"ver":false,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ret":true,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":true,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4QWcRNUcRMAmrDNn","name":"无尽迷宫号角 Horn of the Endless Maze","type":"equipment","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/inventory/horn.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>这个物品着类似于@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.D63FB5D6283927AB]{青铜瓦尔哈拉号角 Bronze Horn of Valhalla}的力量，只是召唤出 的英灵来自深渊，并且看上去像是牛头人一般。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDMM","quantity":1,"weight":2,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4YLIQ267JpGzRgzm","name":"凛冬魔杖 Wand of Winter","type":"consumable","img":"icons/weapons/wands/wand-gem-teal.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这根魔杖看起来和摸起来都像是一根冰柱。你必须之同调才能使用它。</p>\n<p>魔杖有 7 发充能，用来作为施展其内法术的能量。你在持 握该魔杖时，可以用你的动作从魔杖施展下列法术之一：@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.tJzKo2vpEhXZfuJO]{冷冻射线 Ray of Frost}（无充能，或 1 充能作为 5 环法术施展：远程法术攻击命中+5）、@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.InxRn0MsZsH5wslj]{雪雨暴 Sleet Storm}（3 充能：法术豁免 DC 15）或是@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.u2MG84qW8YLuECHa]{冰风暴 Ice Storm}（4 充能：法术豁免 DC 15）。所有这些法术都无需任何法术成分。</p>\n<p>每日黎明时分魔杖将回复[[/r 1d6+1]]的充能，若你耗尽魔杖的最后一发充能，骰一次[[/r d20]]。骰值为 20 时，魔杖融化并永久损坏。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"HotDQ","quantity":1,"weight":null,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":7,"max":"7","per":"charges","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"wand"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4bH0EBZKB1300JvA","name":"猴舞果 Dancing Monkey Fruit","type":"consumable","img":"icons/consumables/fruit/mang-unripe-yellow-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<p>这是楚尔特当地不同寻常的野生动植物。熟练自然技能的冒险者能够一眼认出这些动植物，并通过一个成功 的 DC 15 的智力(自然)检定来回忆起它的详细属性。如果冒险者们是楚尔特本地人，则该检定具优势。</p>\n<p>此处描述的野生动植物可以在南扎路港和其他聚居地内以动植物价格表内对应的价格进行买卖。</p>\n<p>有的野生动植物中会使生物承受一小时或更久的中毒状态。请记住，@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.I1C2EQxwynPd7dOC]{次级复原术 Lesser Restoration}以及类似魔法可以结束该状态。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>这些稀有魔法果实的汁液足以装满一个小瓶。任何吃下猴舞果或者饮下其汁液的类人生物都必须进行一次 DC 14 的体质豁免豁免失败则开始跳起持续一分钟的滑稽舞蹈。免疫中毒的类人生物同样免疫该魔法效果。</p>\n<p>舞者必须耗尽他的移动力在原地跳舞，其攻击检定和敏捷豁免均具劣势。对他发动的攻击检定具优势。每次受到伤害时，舞者可以再次进行该豁免，豁免成功则结束舞蹈效果。当舞蹈效果结束时，该类人生物陷入一小时的中毒状态中。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":5,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":14,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"food"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4w6XiZSpWSj521ur","name":"烈焰符文之琼 Opal of the Lld Rune","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-rough-drop-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这块三角形的火蛋白石每边大约有三寸长，厚度约一寸半。Ild（火）符文在其核心处闪烁，使其摸起来有些温暖。这块蛋白石具有以下特性，这些特性只在此蛋白石装备在你身上时才能生效。</p>\n<p><strong>点燃Ignite</strong>。以一个动作，你可以点燃10尺内的一个物件。该物件必须是可燃的，并且燃起的火堆直径不会高过1尺。</p>\n<p><strong>火焰之友Fire's Friend</strong>。你对寒冷伤害具有抗性。</p>\n<p><strong>火焰驯服者Fire Tamer</strong>。以一个动作，你可以熄灭10尺内的任何明火。你选择半径范围内有多少火焰被熄灭。</p>\n<p><strong>火焰之赠礼Gift of Flame</strong>。通过用你的手指在一件非魔法物品——一把武器或一件盔甲上描摹ild符文，你可以将蛋白石的魔法转移到上面。转移需要花费8小时时间，并且需要两件物品在此期间互相间隔在5尺之内。在这8小时结束时，蛋白石会被摧毁，并且红色的符文会出现在你所选择的物品上，这会使得该物品获得一项基于其形态的增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>武器Weapon</strong>。该武器现在成为一件非普通的魔法武器，它会对任何被它命中的目标造成额外[[/r 1d6]]点火焰伤害。</li>\n<li><strong>盔甲Armor</strong>。该盔甲现在成为一件珍稀的魔法物品，需要同调。穿戴此盔甲时，你对寒冷伤害具有抗性。</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SKT","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5MhoNTRATgN8ScRX","name":"地狱火鞭 Hellfire Whip","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/whip.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + @mod","slashing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"whip","properties":{"fin":true,"rch":true,"amm":false,"hvy":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false,"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5NWdED9qFIbQxlXP","name":"龙之守护  Dragonguard","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-collared-steel-grey.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>穿着这件护甲时你的 AC 额外 + 1。</p>\n<p>这件+1 胸甲 Breastplate 上有 一个金龙的纹样。是由无冬城一位名叫特尔忒冈 Tergon 的人 类英雄所创，它可以令其着装者抵抗龙族吐息攻击时进行的豁免检定具有优势。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LMoP","quantity":1,"weight":20,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":15,"type":"medium","dex":2},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"breastplate","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5gDItLp0f8yymPj6","name":"刺尾狮甲胄 Scorpion Armor","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-banded-simple-leather-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这套板甲是有巨蝎尾狮的几丁壳制成的。穿戴此护甲时，你获得如下增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>这套护甲提升了你的战斗准备，只要你没有陷入失能就获得+5的先攻权调整。</li>\n<li>这套护甲不会对你的敏捷（隐匿）检定造成劣势。</li>\n<li>这套护甲不会在抵抗极度高温的检定骰对你造成劣势。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>诅咒 Curse</strong>。这套护甲被诅咒了。无论穿脱，你都要进行一次DC15的体质豁免检定，失败会受到100（[[/r 10d10+45]]）的毒素伤害，成功则伤害减半。只有@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xjn6gjItpWpldE53]{祈愿术 Wish}能够一处这套护甲的诅咒。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":65,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"abil","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["10d10+45","poison"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":18,"type":"heavy","dex":0},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":15,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6APKLFFb9pdmO4ch","name":"蛇袍 Robe of Serpents","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/back/mantle-collared-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>蛇袍robe of serpents是一种时髦的丝绸服装，在富有的贵族和已经隐退的刺客中很流行。长袍上装饰着[[/r 1d4+3]]个风格化的蛇纹，颜色鲜艳。</p>\n<p>在你的回合中，以一个附赠动作，你可以把长袍上的一条蛇纹变成一条巨大毒蛇giant poisonous snake。蛇立刻从长袍上落下，滑至你身边一片未被占据的空间，并依照你的先攻数值行动。蛇能分辨出友好的生物和敌对的生物，并攻击后者。蛇会在1小时后，或当蛇的生命值降至0时，或当你遣散它（无需花费任何动作）时伴随着一股无害的烟雾消失。一旦被取下，蛇就不能再回到长袍上。当袍子上所有的蛇都被取下时，该长袍变成一件没有魔法的衣服。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SKT","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d4+3","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"clothing","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6aemSmlbKNc9Aaqe","name":"法术宝石（天青石）Spell Gem (Lapis lazuli)","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-rough-cushion-white.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（部分需同调）</em></p>\n<p>一枚法术宝石可以储存一发任意等级职业相应环阶的法术。你将在得知宝石的属性后知晓其内含法术的具体状况。持握宝石时，若你知晓其内的法术且该法术在你的职业法术列表中，则你可以用一个动作施展该法术。以该方式施展法术时无需与宝石同调也不需要任何法术成分。施法过后，宝石中的法术也随之消散。</p>\n<p>如果宝石里的高环阶法术超过了你当前可施展法术环阶，则你需要以你的施法关键属性进行一次额外的检定，以判断本次施法是否成功。其DC 为10＋该法术的环阶。检定失败时，该法术失效且宝石中的法术也随之消散。</p>\n<p>不同类型的法术宝石 其能够存储法术的最大环阶也各不相同。宝石与法术环阶相关的稀有度和储存法术其豁免DC 与攻击加值，具体如“法术宝石”表所示。</p>\n<p>与宝石同调后，你可以在宝石内未有法术时将一发法术注入其中。此时，你需要手握空的宝石并正常施展一次该法术，然后法术便会注入宝石中而不是正常生效。法术的施法时间必须是 1 动作或不低于 1 分钟时间，且其法术环阶必须不高于宝石的上限。如果该法术是防护系且需要耗材，则你也需要满足相应需求，不过只需一半材料就能完成该作业。</p>\n<p>被注入法术后，同一枚宝石必须在下次黎明过后才能再次向其注入法术。</p>\n<p>这些法术宝石由地底侏儒制作而成，不过他们并不愿意跟别人分享这种秘密工艺。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"5\"><strong>法术宝石</strong></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><strong> 最大法术环价 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 宝石 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 稀有度 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 豁免DC </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 攻击加值 </strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1环</td>\n<td>天青石Lapis lazuli</td>\n<td>非普通</td>\n<td>13</td>\n<td>+5</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"OoTA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6bNNC9MSTRRDUY2K","name":"利爪徽章 Insignia of Claws","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/neck/amulet-carved-stone-purple.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>当你进入战斗状态时，该龙巫教徽章上的宝石会随之发出 紫色的光芒，并以此提升你拳头或其他天生武器的力量。</p>\n<p>着装该徽章时，你以徒手打击和天生武器进行的攻击检定 和伤害掷骰获得 +1 加值。这样的攻击视为带有魔法。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"HotDQ","quantity":1,"weight":null,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6faUjPSdkJlnM9Nj","name":"法尔基尔的固执钢盔 Falkir's Helm of Pigheadedness","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-sallet-horned-grey.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这个钢盔形似野猪头。在@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.cGO3m3Xu4mtPegr4]{侦测魔法 Detect Magic}下，头盔散发出微弱的变化学派灵光。</p>\n<p><strong>诅咒 Curse</strong>。这个头盔拥有诅咒。一旦头盔被带上， 直到穿戴者死亡或被施展@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ewDH2w8w2yLSM021]{移除诅咒 Remove Curse}或类似法术才能被摘下。任何装备该头盔的类人生物都会出现如下缺陷\" 我十分固执，并总是坚信自己是对的。\"(这个缺陷将取代任何与之冲突的缺陷)</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDMM","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[{"_id":"FG4R9B3BihNoIjCw","changes":[{"key":"data.details.flaw","mode":2,"value":"我十分固执，并总是坚信自己是对的。"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/equipment/head/helm-sallet-horned-grey.webp","label":"+ 缺陷","origin":"Item.6faUjPSdkJlnM9Nj","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6gVCkuxAqIeSgg0V","name":"粘球魔杖 Wand of Viscid Globs","type":"consumable","img":"icons/weapons/staves/staff-ornate-purple.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<h4><strong>卓尔制品Drowcraft Items </strong></h4>\n<p>由卓尔制作的（或是由幽暗地域其他种族制作的某些）魔法物品，都是由一些无法接触日光的物质或仪式制成。许多这类物品（包括卓尔的护甲、武器和魔法斗篷之类）当暴露在阳光下超过1小时就会失去其魔力。充能物品则会被彻底摧毁。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>魔杖（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这根卓尔制作的黑细魔杖有7 发充能。持握该魔杖时，你可以用一个动作并消耗1 发充能，向身边60 尺范围内的一个目标发射一个粘球。对该目标进行一次远程攻击检定，其攻击加值为你的熟练加值加你的施法关键属性调整值（没有施法关键属性时按智力调整值算）。若命中，则粘球炸开并在目标身上凝固，以此使目标受束缚1 小时。时间过后，其身上的粘性物质自然破裂脱落。</p>\n<p>被困目标可以至少一品脱剂量的酒精使其身上的粘质溶解，@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.76A53FC1DC160E02]{灵化之油 Oil of Etherealness}或@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.6BC1A57F655FB594]{万溶剂 Universal Solvent}也可以实现同样的效果。其粘质暴露在阳光下时也会立即溶解。</p>\n<p>此外的其他非魔法手段都无法移除魔杖产生的粘性物质。</p>\n<p>每日午夜时，魔杖会恢复[[/r 1d6+1]]发充能。当你用掉魔杖最后一发充能时骰一次[[/r d20]]，若骰值为1，则魔杖将随之融化为一滩软泥而彻底摧毁。</p>\n<p>粘球魔杖在阳光下连续暴露超过1个小时便会魔力尽失。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"OoTA","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":7,"max":"7","per":"charges","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":"-10-@mod+ @attributes.spelldc+@attributes.prof","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d6+1","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"wand"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6r7p4QaVM7GnMNzX","name":"雷亚斯根茎 Ryath Root","type":"consumable","img":"icons/consumables/vegetable/root-carrot-yellow.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<p>这是楚尔特当地不同寻常的野生动植物。熟练自然技能的冒险者能够一眼认出这些动植物，并通过一个成功 的 DC 15 的智力(自然)检定来回忆起它的详细属性。如果冒险者们是楚尔特本地人，则该检定具优势。</p>\n<p>此处描述的野生动植物可以在南扎路港和其他聚居地内以动植物价格表内对应的价格进行买卖。</p>\n<p>有的野生动植物中会使生物承受一小时或更久的中毒状态。请记住，@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.I1C2EQxwynPd7dOC]{次级复原术 Lesser Restoration}以及类似魔法可以结束该状态。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>吃下雷亚斯根茎的任何生物都会获得 [[/r 2d4]] 点临时生命值。在 24 小时内服用超过一块雷亚斯根茎的生物需要进行一个 DC 13 的 体质豁免，豁免失败则陷入持续一小时的中毒状态。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":50,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d4","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":13,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"food"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"70Fdi3lETOkPVWv8","name":"黑龙面具 Black Dragon Mask","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/mask-horned-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这具以抛光黑檀木制成的带角面具其造型如同一个长角 的颅骨。面具会调整自身尺寸以便其同调者着装。你与之同调并着装后，可以使用下列各属性。</p>\n<p><strong>伤害吸收 Damage Absorption。</strong> 你对强酸伤害拥有抗性， 如果你已经从另一来源拥有了强酸伤害的抗性，则你改为对强酸伤害免疫。若你此前已从另一来源获得了强酸伤害免疫，则你在受到强酸伤害时，可恢复其伤害量一半的生命值。</p>\n<p><strong>龙形威严 Draconic Majesty。</strong>你未着装护甲时，可以将自己的魅力加值加入你的护甲等级中。</p>\n<p><strong>龙息 Dragon Breath。</strong>若你有本身拥有需要休息充能的吐息武器，则该吐息改为充能 6。</p>\n<p><strong>龙之视界 Dragon Sight。</strong>你获得 60 尺的黑暗视觉，若你已拥有黑暗视觉，则其范围再增加 60 尺。你每日有一次机会， 可获得持续 5 分钟的 30 尺的盲视感官。</p>\n<p><strong>龙言 Dragon Tongue。</strong>你可以说和理解龙语。你对黑龙进行的所有魅力检定都具有优势。</p>\n<p><strong>传奇抗性 Legendary Resistance（1/日）。</strong>你进行一次豁免检定失败时，可以选择将其改为豁免成功。</p>\n<p><strong>水下呼吸 Water Breathing。</strong>你可以在水下呼吸。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"HotDQ","quantity":1,"weight":null,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"clothing","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"7Oj1cdSHP2vLOSvj","name":"古特巨斧 Gurt's Greataxe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-battle.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>在冰斧之年（123DR），霜巨人领主古特败在了乌斯伽·加多弗森——后来成为乌斯伽野蛮人的那些人的首领——的手下。这场战斗标志了人类对德沙林谷的支配力已经胜过了巨人。古特的巨斧被埋在莫格高地，直到它被发掘出来并被带回了深水城。在这座城市的地下墓穴中放置了几十年后，这柄巨斧被赐予了霜巨人哈什纳格，以表彰他为深水城所做的贡献。乌斯伽野蛮人在看到武器时能认出来，并会攻击任何使用它的巨人。</p>\n<p>你用这把魔法武器做出的攻击检定与伤害掷骰获得+1加值。它的体型适合巨人使用，重325磅，每次命中造成[[/r d12]]点挥砍伤害，如果目标是人类则还要额外造成[[/r 2d12]]点挥砍伤害。</p>\n<p>当周围的温度降到华氏0度以下时，斧头会发出火炬般的光。在此状态下这种光芒无法被熄灭。</p>\n<p>以一个动作，你可以施放一个造成寒冷伤害而不是火焰伤害版本的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.tf3EIMrOkbZvOxSz]{灼热金属 Heat Metal}法术（豁免DC13）。一旦此能力被使用，则直到下个黎明之前都不能被再次使用。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SKT","quantity":1,"weight":325,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"1","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["3d12 + @mod+1","slashing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"2d12","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"greataxe","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"mgc":true,"lgt":false,"two":true,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":true,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8AAB6cf7qNWsCxoC","name":"凛冬指环 Ring of Winter","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-cabochon-gold.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>指环（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>Artus Cimber 拥有这一物品已经超过一个世纪了。凛冬指环是一个黄金圆环，会根据佩戴者的手指尺寸改变大小紧密贴合。一层薄霜覆于戒指外层，正常的温度无法将其融化。这一指环摸上去冰冷刺骨，并且会在刚开始时让佩戴的手失去知觉，但同调完成后这一冰冷就不再被感知到。</p>\n<p>凛冬指环拥有智能，会尝试控制佩戴它的任意生物，如果它成功了，它会控制佩戴者对周围的一切人与物造成恶劣伤害，并会试图挑起敌人的怒火，无情地带领它的佩戴者走向毁灭。</p>\n<p><strong>智能 Sentience</strong>。凛冬指环的智能为混乱邪恶，智力14，感知14，魅力17。这枚指环通过向携带者或佩戴者传输情感进行沟通，它拥有正常听力以及60尺正常视力。这枚戒指渴求毁灭，喜欢不分情况向其他人施加伤害。</p>\n<p><strong>无法检测 Nondetection</strong>。凛冬指环蔑视一切试图通过魔法定位它的尝试。无论是置换本身还是穿戴者都无法被预言法术定位，也无法通过魔法预言道具进行观察。</p>\n<p><strong>冻结时间 Frozen Time</strong>。只要你带着指环，你就不会自然老去。这一效应类似于假死状态，戒指被移除并不会导致你避过的时间立刻回馈给你。这个指环并不能使佩戴者巫师魔法或是超自然的老化效果，比如说幽魂的恐惧面容。</p>\n<p><strong>冷冻免疫 Cold Immunity</strong>。当完成同调并佩戴指环时，你对冷冻伤害免疫，亦不会再经受任何极度严寒导致的力竭状态。</p>\n<p><strong>魔法 Magic</strong>。凛冬指环具有十二次充能，每天都会在黎明重新完全充能。戴着戒指时，你可以使用必要数量的充能发动如下特性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你可以以一个动作花费一次充能降低120尺球形范围内的温度，球心为三百尺内视线所及之处。这片区域内每分钟会下降二十华氏度，最低可以降至-30华氏度。一旦温度下降至32度以下就会在表面形成冰洁和霜冻。这一效应在你不使用戒指以一个动作结束效应之前永久保持，结束后这片区域的温度会以每分钟10度回升至正常。</li>\n<li>你可以通过消耗必要数量的充能从指环施放如下法术（法术豁免DC17）：@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.naXxMtlZiJr9JYdU]{毕格比之手}（Bigby’s Hand,两次充能，这个巨手由冰霜构成，免疫冰冻伤害，使用金刚拳时造成钝击伤害而非力场伤害），@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.z9HXB89B3uO5NHW8]{寒冰锥}（两次充能），@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.oLtyOvrWeLNEJDIE]{冰化术}（三次充能，类似石化术效应，但是将目标变为具有石质的密度和耐久的冰），@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.u2MG84qW8YLuECHa]{冰风暴}（两次充能），@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.7ogt8uGRk3Ts8fXZ]{欧提路克冰封法球}（三次充能），@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.InxRn0MsZsH5wslj]{雪雨暴}（一次充能），@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.1oL8DBOVZMuhaKpw]{荆棘丛生}（一次充能；棘刺由冰构成）或者@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.kZ9PSqGyiR7bGViM]{冰墙术}（两次充能）。</li>\n<li>你可以以一个动作花费必要的充能创造一个无生命的的冰制物件（两次充能）或是具有生命的冰霜生物（四次充能）。这个冰制物品不具有任何可以动的部件，且必须能够容纳于10尺的方格之中，同时具有金属或石头的密度与耐久（这由你决定）。冰霜生物必须以CR2或以下的野兽为模板。这个冰霜生物具有原模板野兽的数据，但是有如下变更：这一生命是对火焰具有易伤的构装体，对寒冷和毒素伤害免疫，并免疫下列效应：魅惑、力竭、恐慌、麻痹、石化以及中毒。这个冰霜生物只遵从创造者的指令。这个冰制物件或是冰霜生物会在你六十尺内未被占据的空间出现。它会在二十四小时或是生命值归零后融化成一滩正常的水。在极度炎热条件下，它会每分钟失去5（[[/r 1d10]]）点生命值。在必要情况下，用DMG第八章的指引来决定无生命物件的生命值。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>其他特性 Other Properties</strong>。根据传言，凛冬指环具有一些只能由一个不会被指环破坏其意志的邪恶存在才能发动的特性。霜巨人始终相信这枚指环可以冻结整个世界，而一个侍奉卡林珊帕夏pasha的风巨灵层宣扬这妹纸换可以用于召唤并控制白龙，也可以用于强大的原初者 Iceprimordial 克瑞欧纳克斯。</p>\n<p><strong>摧毁指环 Destroying the Ring</strong>。这枚指环近乎不可摧毁，即便是最强烈的魔法高温也能抵抗。如果它被戴在最强大的至高妖精，也就是夏之女王的手上，这枚戒指将会融化，然后被永远摧毁。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":true,"rarity":"artifact","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":120,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":300,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":12,"max":"12","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":true},"effects":[{"label":"+ 冷冻抗性","icon":"icons/equipment/finger/ring-cabochon-gold.webp","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.di.value","mode":2,"value":"cold"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"tint":null,"transfer":true,"flags":{},"_id":"ry4mj3y03vzu5h6e"}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8XdOjEiwP2oJM7rc","name":"开辟者 Waythe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/greatsword-guard-gold-worn.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这把独一无二的巨剑的前一位所有者是个高位的云巨人cloud giant。你用该魔法武器发动的攻击检定和伤害掷骰具+1 加值。你用它击中一个种类为“巨人giant”的生物时，目标生物将受额外的[[/r 2d6]]的挥砍伤害，且必须成功通过一次DC 15 的力量豁免，否则陷入倒地状态。</p>\n<p>这把剑还能实现@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.04362F9153D7CAED]{侦敌魔杖 Wand of Enemy Detection}的效果。它在每日黎明时恢复所有已消耗充能，且不会在充能耗尽时被摧毁。</p>\n<p><strong>智能Sentience</strong>。开辟者是一把中立善良的智能魔法武器。它的智力为12，感知2，魅力14。它听觉和黑暗视觉的感官范围是120 尺。这把武器能够说、读和理解巨人语及通用语，同时还能够与持用者通过心灵感应进行交流。</p>\n<p><strong>个性Personality</strong>。这把剑信奉自由，认为人们可以自由选择他们觉得合适的生活方式。他会护卫自己的朋友，而且还乐意与志同道合的持有者成为朋友。（善良阵营角色只需 1 分钟便能与之完成同调。）开辟者英勇无畏，甚至有些莽撞，因而会建议大胆地采取行动。它很可能会与邪恶或胆小的持用者进行产生冲突。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TftYP","quantity":1,"weight":6,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":true,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":7,"max":"7","per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"+1","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d6+1+@mod","slashing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"2d6","save":{"ability":"str","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"greatsword","properties":{"hvy":true,"two":true,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"lgt":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":true,"attuned":true,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8hl07uKQbW6Bj8um","name":"呜咔坚果 Wukka Nuts","type":"consumable","img":"icons/consumables/nuts/walnut-shell-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<p>这是楚尔特当地不同寻常的野生动植物。熟练自然技能的冒险者能够一眼认出这些动植物，并通过一个成功 的 DC 15 的智力(自然)检定来回忆起它的详细属性。如果冒险者们是楚尔特本地人，则该检定具优势。</p>\n<p>此处描述的野生动植物可以在南扎路港和其他聚居地内以动植物价格表内对应的价格进行买卖。</p>\n<p>有的野生动植物中会使生物承受一小时或更久的中毒状态。请记住，@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.I1C2EQxwynPd7dOC]{次级复原术 Lesser Restoration}以及类似魔法可以结束该状态。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>这些拳头大小的坚果生长在呜咔树上，不巧的是，这种树也是幻色蛇、苏怪和佐博怪偏爱的巢穴。晃动呜咔坚果时，它会咔咔作响，果壳发出 10 尺的明亮光照，并延伸出 10 尺的微光光照。该魔法光线在一分钟后熄灭，但是再摇动会使这种光线重新照亮。如果呜咔坚果被撬开了，它就会失去魔法效果。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":1,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":null,"condition":"晃动。"},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"food"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8wd2Gde69F3I2ZGD","name":"纠缠魔杖 Wand of Entangle","type":"consumable","img":"icons/weapons/staves/staff-simple-hooked.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需施法者同调）</em></p>\n<p>这把魔杖有 7 发充能。持握此魔杖时，你可以用一个动作并消耗 1 发充能以其施展@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.NZ4JOGBMJzeCKT5O]{纠缠术 Entangle}（豁免DC 15）。</p>\n<p>该魔杖每日黎明时恢复[[/r 1d6+1]]发已消耗充能。充能耗尽时骰一次[[/r d20]]。若骰值为1，则魔杖化为灰烬而毁灭。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TftYP","quantity":1,"weight":null,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":7,"max":"7","per":"day","autoDestroy":false,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d20","save":{"ability":"str","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"wand","attuned":true,"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9GZprWgWlJBFQQqS","name":"欺诈者眼罩 Knave's Eye Patch","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/goggles-leather-grey.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物(需同调)</em></p>\n<p>佩戴此眼罩时，你获得以下好处:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你在依赖视觉的感知(察觉)检定上具有优势。</li>\n<li>如果你有日光敏感 sunlightsensitivity 特性，则该特性无效。</li>\n<li>你对阅读你思想或侦测你是否说谎的魔法效果免 疫。只有在你同意时，其他生物才能用心灵感应和你交流。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDH","quantity":1,"weight":null,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9KO1BQjBOPfNTXsD","name":"鲜血之石 Blod Stone","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-rough-cushion-red-white.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这颗钻石含有一个生物的血液——血液在其中以blod（鲜血）符文的形式出现。当你携带此物品时，你可以用你的动作来预测一个与物品所含血液有关的、离你最近且并非不死生物的生物的位置。你可以感应到这个生物相对于你的距离和方向。该生物可以是该物品中血液的主人，或者是血亲。</p>\n<p>这件物品由一颗价值5000金币的大钻石制成。当一个生物的血液在制作该物品的过程中被倒在钻石上时，血液会流进宝石的中心。如果宝石被摧毁，血液便会蒸发并永久地消失。一个复仇者可能会用鲜血之石 Blod Stone 来追猎一整个血亲家族。这种石头有时也会被作为礼物送给兄弟姐妹，或者由父母传给孩子。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SKT","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9wXUCUa7z6KE1GRB","name":"负载石 Loadstone","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-rough-pendeloque-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>这块石头是一枚价值150 gp 的大宝石。</p>\n<p><strong>诅咒Curse</strong>。这块石头受到了诅咒，但它的魔法本质却被隐藏起来，@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.cGO3m3Xu4mtPegr4]{侦测魔法 Detect Magic}无法对其生效，但用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.tyshE8ZcV1Xniej3]{鉴定术 Identify}却可以鉴别其本质。若你在携带这块石头时执行“疾走Dash”或“撤离Disengage”动作，则其诅咒将被激活。只要诅咒还在生效，你的速度减少 5 尺，且最大载重和最大抬举磅数减半。即便如此，你也不愿丢弃这块石头。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TftYP","quantity":1,"weight":150,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[{"_id":"RzIPTrflQdUCDumR","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.walk","mode":2,"value":"-5"}],"disabled":true,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-rough-pendeloque-blue.webp","label":"速度 -5","origin":"Item.9wXUCUa7z6KE1GRB","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"AlhbdYUh4hLYcZca","name":"地狱火巨斧 Hellfire Greataxe","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/greataxe.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":7,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d12 + @mod","slashing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"greataxe","properties":{"hvy":true,"two":true,"amm":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"ver":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false,"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"AtInOp1Se2hkwun4","name":"焰袭 Tinders Trike","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-ritual-black.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<h4><strong>元素武器Elemental Weapons </strong></h4>\n<p>领导邪恶元素教会的四位先知每人都拥有强大的元素武器。这些强大的物体被注入了邪恶元素亲王的本质。除了作为武器在战斗中明显的用处外，它们还可以作为钥匙，让先知们引导元素节点的力量，撕开两个位面之间的边界。武器也使持握兵器的人心生恶念，将恶人的本质显露出来。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>作为一把燧石匕首，焰袭有着极为奇特的形状，它的刀刃异常锋利，当它击中坚硬的物体时，它的边缘就会迸发出火花。刀柄摸上去总是很温暖，刀刃在使用后会闷烧[[/r 1d4]]分钟。它融入了邪恶的火元素亲王伊米希的火花。</p>\n<p>你用这个魔法武器进行的攻击和伤害检定有+2加值。当你用它造成伤害时，目标会受到额外的[[/r 2d6]]火焰伤害。</p>\n<p><strong>火元素掌控Fire Mastery</strong>。当你持握焰袭时，你可以获得以下好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你可以流利地使用火族语。</li>\n<li>你对火焰伤害有抗性。</li>\n<li>你可以对火元素施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.f63uBXNvbalm1y7v]{支配怪物 Dominate Monster}(DC17)。一旦你如此做，焰袭就不能再次使用此能力，直到第二天黎明。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>焚世烈焰之舞Dance of the All-Consuming Fire</strong>。当位于一个火元素节点内时，你可以执行一个名为“焚世烈焰之舞”的仪式，使用焰袭制造一个火之毁灭法球(参见毁灭法球对仪式时间和成本的描述)。一旦你执行了这个仪式，焰袭就不能再被用于执行这个仪式，直到第二天黎明。</p>\n<p><strong>缺陷Flaw</strong>。焰袭让持用者急躁和鲁莽。当你与这把武器同调，你就会有以下缺点：“我做事不加思考，冒险不考虑后果。”</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PotA","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"2","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + @mod + 2","piercing"],["2d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d4","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"dagger","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":true,"mgc":true,"lgt":true,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":true,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"BLliI6tHwbQsBdMz","name":"吉他独奏匕首 Dagger of Guitar Solos","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/dagger.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这把卓尔制造的匕首上面有银色的网状装饰。在打斗后或者与敌人战斗时，匕首会神奇的发出吉他独奏的声音片段。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDMM","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":750,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"dex","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4+@mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"dagger","properties":{"fin":true,"lgt":true,"thr":true,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Bh9Qy0t6hCk4AVoq","name":"热能方块 Thermal Cube","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/treasure/puzzle-cube.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>这个3立方寸大小的固体硫磺石可以产生足量的干热，以此将15尺范围内的气温保持在95华氏度（35摄氏度）。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"IDRotF","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"perm"},"target":{"value":15,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"BhCdcFj0tUCj3m14","name":"驱虫剂（熏香块）Insect Repellent (block of incense)","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/stone/ore-pile-teal.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在南扎路港可以买到两种形式的驱虫剂：熏香块或药膏。贸易亲王克薇欧泽垄断着这两样物品的销售。两种驱虫剂都无法驱离带“巨”字前缀的昆虫或肮脏的昆虫集群。</p>\n<p>一块熏香的售价为 1 sp。点燃后，它能燃烧 8 小时，并驱离半径 20 尺内的普通昆虫。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0.1,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":false,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":8,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":20,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"ammo","attuned":false,"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"CakcoI5ALchCz0ku","name":"扎瑞尔之剑 Sword of Zariel","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-gold-holy.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需由一名此剑认为值得之生物同调）</em></p>\n<p>此长剑在天使Zariel失宠之前属于她，该剑由天界钢制成，它发出微弱的光芒和嗡嗡的声音。由这件武器选择谁能与之同调，谁不能。它渴望持有者能体现出勇敢和英雄主义。</p>\n<p><strong>同调Attunement</strong>。此剑允许你立即进行同调，而不需要一次短休。当你第一次与之同调时，你被转化为一个神圣的，理想中的自我，被超凡脱俗的美包围，充斥着一抹天堂的气息。无论是魔法还是神的干预都无法逆转这种变化。你的阵营变为守序善良，你获得以下特征：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>天使语言Angelic Language</strong>。你会说，读，写天界语。</li>\n<li><strong>天界抗力Celestial Resistance</strong>。你对光耀伤害和黯蚀伤害有抗性。</li>\n<li><strong>神圣存在Divine Presence</strong>。你的魅力值变成20，除非它已经为20或更高。</li>\n<li><strong>羽翅Feathered Wings</strong>。你长出一对美丽的羽毛翅膀，赋予你90尺的飞行速度和悬停的能力。如果你已经有了不同种类的翅膀，这些新翅膀会取代旧的翅膀。</li>\n<li><strong>真实视觉True sight</strong>。你的眼睛变成明亮的银池。你可以看穿普通与魔法的黑暗，看到隐形的生物和物件，自觉检测出幻象并在对抗它们的豁免上自动成功，在60尺的范围内感知到变形生物或被魔法改变的生物的原始形态，并看到以太位面Ethereal Plane。</li>\n<li><strong>新个性New Personality</strong>。你获得了新的性格特征，通过在下面的表格上掷一次骰子来决定。这些特质凌驾于任何冲突的人格特质、理想、羁绊或缺陷之上。\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\" colspan=\"2\">人格特质 Personality Traits</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>[[/r d8]]</strong></th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>人格特质</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>我尊重所有人，包括敌人。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>我不会说谎。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>我喜欢和别人分享我的哲学世界观和经验。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>每次谈话我都直奔主题。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>我经常引用（或错误引用）宗教文献。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>当我目睹残忍或不公正时，我很快会生气。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>我的赞美和信任是赢得来的，而不是无偿给予的。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>我喜欢一切整洁有序。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\" colspan=\"2\">理念 Ideals</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>[[/r d6]]</strong></th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>理念</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>宽容Charity。我总是帮助那些需要帮助的人。（善良）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>信念Faith。我选择严格遵守一位合法善神的信条。（守序）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>责任Responsibility。保护弱者是强者的责任。（守序）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4.</td>\n<td>尊重Respect。 所有人都应被尊敬对待。（守序）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>荣誉Honor。我的行为方式决定了我死后的回报。（守序）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>救赎Redemption。所有的生物都有能力变得更好。（善良）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\" colspan=\"2\">羁绊Bonds</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>[[/r d6]]</strong></th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>羁绊</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>我有一首我经常哼唱的宗教赞美诗。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>我必须把我的信仰和我所见证的罪恶记录下来。完成后，这本书将是我给多元宇宙的礼物。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>虽然我只在梦中见过这个田园小镇，但我对ldyllglen仍怀有美好的回忆。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>我愿意为身边的战友而死，无论他们有什么过错。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>无论在哪，只要我找到恶魔和其他邪恶的人，就设法去摧毁他们，以此来纪念天使Zariel。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>扎瑞尔之剑选择了我。 我应当用它来替天行道。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\" colspan=\"2\">缺陷Flaws</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>[[/r d6]]</strong></th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>缺陷</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>我太轻易评判别人。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>我太容易宽恕别人。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>为了更大的利益，我愿意牺牲无辜的生命。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>缺陷？什么缺陷？我是完美的。彻底的完美！</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>我不允许任何东西阻挡我从多元宇宙根除邪恶的征途。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>我不理会那些不支持我计划的人，因为我的使命高于一切。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"artifact","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":