{"_id":"D2QvBcY8voHBOSDU","name":"厄运石 Stone of Ill Luck","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-faceted-rough-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>任何试图鉴定这块抛光玛瑙agate的人都会以为这是一块@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.4C74DC315404B07F]{幸运石 Stone of Good Luck (Luckstone)}，而它也的确会为携带者提供该物品的增益效果。</p>\n<p><strong>诅咒Curse</strong>。把这件被诅咒物品带在身上时，你的属性检定和豁免检定承受 -2 罚值。在诅咒被发现前，DM 将偷偷应用这一惩罚，假装你只获得增益效应。只要诅咒仍在生效，你就会不愿与它分开。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TftYP","quantity":1,"weight":0.1,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":true,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":true},"effects":[{"label":"Saving Throw Bonus","icon":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","changes":[{"key":"data.bonuses.abilities.save","mode":2,"value":"‒2","priority":7}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"tint":null,"transfer":true,"flags":{},"_id":"ok1wlf610trok5mm"},{"label":"Ability Check Bonus","icon":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","changes":[{"key":"data.bonuses.abilities.check","mode":2,"value":"‒2","priority":7}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"tint":null,"transfer":true,"flags":{},"_id":"r2xsn9ds1jh7lkfj"}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DD59gkW3DoKETJSE","name":"地狱火矛 Hellfire Spear","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/spear.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6 + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":"1d8 + @mod"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"spear","properties":{"thr":true,"ver":true,"amm":false,"hvy":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"two":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false,"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DMS847iAI66tfM4k","name":"地狱火长矛 Hellfire Pike","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/pike.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":18,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d10 + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"pike","properties":{"hvy":true,"rch":true,"two":true,"amm":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"ver":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false,"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DzAaqND1dJnJ03Iz","name":"水溺 Drown","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/trident-curved-steel.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<h4><strong>元素武器Elemental Weapons </strong></h4>\n<p>领导邪恶元素教会的四位先知每人都拥有强大的元素武器。这些强大的物体被注入了邪恶元素亲王的本质。除了作为武器在战斗中明显的用处外，它们还可以作为钥匙，让先知们引导元素节点的力量，撕开两个位面之间的边界。武器也使持握兵器的人心生恶念，将恶人的本质显露出来。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这是一把钢制三叉戟，在它柄的上部装饰有青铜藤壶，柄的末端有一颗海绿色的宝石和一个银色的贝壳。如果它掉到水面上，它会浮在水面上而非沉下去；如果它被留在水下，它会悬浮在原地。三叉戟的触感总是冰凉的，而且它不会因为暴露在水中而受到任何伤害。水溺内部融入奥莉德拉——邪恶的水元素亲王——的一个火花。</p>\n<p>你用这个魔法武器进行的攻击和伤害检定有+1加值。当你用它造成伤害时，目标会受到额外的[[/r 1d8]]冷冻伤害。</p>\n<p><strong>水元素掌控Water Mastery</strong>。当你持握水溺时，你会得到以下好处:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你能流利地说水族语。</li>\n<li>你对冷冻伤害有抗性。</li>\n<li>你可以对水元素施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.f63uBXNvbalm1y7v]{支配怪物 Dominate Monster}（DC17）。一旦你如此做，水溺不能再次使用此能力，直到第二天黎明。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>无尽痛苦之泪Tears of Endless Anguish</strong>。当位于一个水元素节点内时，你可以执行一个名为“无尽痛苦之泪”的仪式，使用水溺来创建一个水之毁灭法球(参见毁灭法球对仪式时间和成本的描述)。一旦你执行了这个仪式，水溺就不能再被用来再次执行这个仪式，直到第二天黎明。</p>\n<p><strong>缺陷Flaw</strong>。水溺使持用者贪婪。当你同调该武器，你得到以下缺陷：“我要求而且理应得到最大份额的战利品，我拒绝放弃我的任何东西。”此外，如果你同调水溺连续24小时以上，藤壶就会在你的皮肤上形成。藤壶可以用一个@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.7dqplcsKNYQgRh2S]{高等复原术 Greater Restoration}或类似的魔法移除，但不能在你同调武器的状态下移除。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PotA","quantity":1,"weight":4,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"1","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6+@mod+1","piercing"],["1d8","cold"]],"versatile":"1d8 + @mod + 1"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"trident","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":true,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"mgc":true,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":true,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"E6PdYTEm1EOyLjzO","name":"驱虫剂（药膏）Insect Repellent (greasy salve)","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/materials/bowl-powder-teal.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在南扎路港可以买到两种形式的驱虫剂:熏香块或药膏。贸易 亲王克薇欧泽垄断着这两样物品的销售。两种驱虫剂都无法驱离带“巨”字前缀的昆虫或肮 脏的昆虫集群。</p>\n<p>药膏为葫芦装或瓶装，一葫芦/一瓶的售价为 1gp，内含 20 剂无味油膏。一剂药膏能保护涂抹者 24 小时内不受普通昆虫伤 害。该药膏是防水的，所以不会被雨水冲走。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":1,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":false,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":24,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":20,"max":"20","per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"ammo","attuned":false,"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"E73ep2MPJmhDhTeX","name":"地狱火重弩 Hellfire Heavy Crossbow","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/crossbow-heavy.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":18,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":100,"long":400,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d10 + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialR","baseItem":"heavycrossbow","properties":{"amm":true,"hvy":true,"two":true,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"ver":false,"lod":true,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ECA5Yu8JCRjsJd6V","name":"阿格哈荣的龙之法杖 Dragon staff of Ahghairon","type":"consumable","img":"icons/weapons/wands/wand-carved-fire.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>法杖(需同调)</em></p>\n<p>持握阿格哈荣的龙之法杖时，你在对抗巨龙的法术或 喷吐武器，以及其他龙类生物(例如龙龟 dragon turtles) 的喷吐武器的豁免上具有优势。</p>\n<p>被你用龙之法杖触碰过的龙类生物可以无视阿格哈荣的禁龙结界 Ahghairon's dragonward 进入深水城。此效果持续到该生物再次被龙之法杖触碰，或持续到你在给予此效果时预设的时 间结束时。</p>\n<p>这把法杖有 10 发充能。持握法杖时，你可以用一个 动作并消耗 1 发充能以施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Ja6HpsLeGA9MQ0Rm]{命令术 Command}。如果你选 择一条龙为目标，则它在豁免上承受劣势。法杖每天在黎 明时恢复[[/r 1d10]]发充能。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDH","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":10,"max":"10","per":"charges","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d10","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"wand"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"EMgYhjNXzeY8qKUM","name":"贝希默之失落王冠 Lost Grown of Besilmer","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-norman-engraved.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<h4><strong>贝希默之遗物Relics of Besilmer</strong></h4>\n<p>该物品是贝希默的矮人们为他们的国王托希尔德·焰舌（Torhild Flametongue）制作。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这顶矮人战盔是一顶坚固的开面式钢盔，额头上方装饰着一个金色的圆环，上面有七根金色的尖刺冠。当你穿戴这顶王冠时，你获得以下好处</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你具有对心灵伤害的抗性。</li>\n<li>你在对抗魅惑的豁免检定上具有优势。</li>\n<li>你可以使用一个附赠动作来激励一个你能看见的、离你60尺以内的、能看见或听见你的生物。在你下一次回合结束前，受激励的生物可以掷出一个[[/r d6]]，并将掷出的数字加到它所做的一个属性检定、攻击检定或豁免检定中。这将消耗王冠的1发充能。它有3发充能，并且在每天黎明恢复[[/r 1d3]]发。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PotA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"能看见。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"3","per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d3","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"EQRJpwKgpiDUnudq","name":"光明使者 Lightbringer","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-flanged-steel-grey.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这件 +1 硬头锤 mace是为晨曦之神洛山达 Lathander 麾下某位牧师订制的，曾是晨曦之主洛山达的祭司所有。其是由凡戴尔协定的魔法师与侏儒及矮人们共同完成的杰作。锤的头部由 坚实的黄铜制成，并塑形为旭日的样式。这把名为光明使者的武器可以依其持用者的指示变得如火炬般明亮。其散发光耀 时还可以对不死生物额外造成[[/r 1d6]]的光耀伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LMoP","quantity":1,"weight":4,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"+1","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6+1+@mod","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"mace","properties":{"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"EhW2gBzYzx8d9s2i","name":"土巨怪之爪 Claws of the Umber Hulk","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/hand/gauntlet-plate-steel-grey.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这些沉重的棕色铁护手被锻造成一个土巨怪的爪子形状，戴着它的人可以套在手和前臂上，一直戴到肘部。当你戴上两个爪子时，你可以获得20尺的挖掘速度，你可以以每轮1尺的速度挖穿坚硬的岩石。</p>\n<p>此外，你可以戴着爪子作为近战武器。你熟练于使用它，它可以在一次攻击中造成[[/r 1d8]]点挥砍伤害（你的力量调整可以正常作用于攻击检定和伤害检定）。</p>\n<p>当你戴着爪子的时候，你不能操纵物体或施放带有躯体成分的法术。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PotA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+@mod","slashing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"clothing","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[{"_id":"aeVNq4jo2aqbhUSk","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.burrow","mode":2,"value":"20"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/equipment/hand/gauntlet-plate-steel-grey.webp","label":"掘穴速度+20尺","origin":"Item.EhW2gBzYzx8d9s2i","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FHgYysVEImXzvnVh","name":"被诅咒的幸运石 Cursed Luckstone","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-faceted-rough-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这颗扁平，灰黑相间的卵石刻着一个未知的神秘符号，触感冰凉。携带这颗石头时，你在你所选择的一项属性检定中获得优势。直到下一个黎明，这颗石头被无法再次使用。</p>\n<p><strong>诅咒 Curse</strong>。这一物品受到诅咒。与它同调会使你被诅咒，直到你被作为目标施展一个@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ewDH2w8w2yLSM021]{移除诅咒 Remove Curse}或类似的法术。在你被诅咒时，你无法抛弃这颗石头，它会立即传送回你的口袋或者包中。当你使用了石头的魔力之后，你之后的两次属性检定具有劣势。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GoS","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FWvR81JWUyvbzz6C","name":"血矛 Blood Spear","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/spear-simple-jagged.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>在施特拉德·冯·扎洛维奇到来之前，无情的酋长喀万 Kavan 和他的部族就已经在巴力诺克山脉生活了数个世纪之久。尽管他是个不折不扣的活人，但喀万与吸血鬼们也有一些共同之处：他白天睡觉，晚上打猎，他喝猎物的鲜血，并在地下生活。在战斗中，他挥舞着一把沾满鲜血的长矛。这就是最初的血矛，这把武器会从被它杀害的生物身上吸取生命力并将之转化为持有者的生命力，给持矛的个体持续战斗下去的耐力。</p>\n<p>当你使用这把魔法矛做出近战攻击并将目标的生命值降低到0点时，你将获得[[/r 2d6]]的临时生命值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CoS","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6 + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":"1d8 + @mod"},"formula":"2d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"spear","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":true,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"mgc":true,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":true,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FXb2Md8C79K5ha9w","name":"疯狂歌德的魔法帽 Maddgoth's Helm","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/hat-pointed-leather-purple.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需类人生物同调）</em></p>\n<p>同调并戴上它之后，就能在疯狂歌德城堡中对所有伤害免疫，包括其顶部和庭院。其头盔若被带离城堡，就会化为灰烬被摧毁、</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDMM","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FebP0mOo7EjvEKk4","name":"红龙面具 Red Dragon Mask","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/mask-horned-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这具光滑的深红色面具有后掠的角和尖锐的颊脊。面具会调整自身尺寸以便其同调者着装。你与之同调并着装后，可以使用下列各属性。</p>\n<p><strong>伤害吸收 Damage Absorption。</strong> 你对火焰伤害拥有抗性， 如果你已经从另一来源拥有了火焰伤害的抗性，则你改为对火焰伤害免疫。若你此前已从另一来源获得了火焰伤害免疫，则你在受到火焰伤害时，可恢复其伤害量一半的生命值。</p>\n<p><strong>龙形威严 Draconic Majesty。</strong>你未着装护甲时，可以将自己的魅力加值加入你的护甲等级中。</p>\n<p><strong>龙息 Dragon Breath。</strong>若你有本身拥有需要休息充能的吐息武器，则该吐息改为充能 6。</p>\n<p><strong>龙之视界 Dragon Sight。</strong>你获得 60 尺的黑暗视觉，若你已拥有黑暗视觉，则其范围再增加 60 尺。你每日有一次机会， 可获得持续 5 分钟的 30 尺的盲视感官。</p>\n<p><strong>龙言 Dragon Tongue。</strong>你可以说和理解龙语。你对黑龙进行的所有魅力检定都具有优势。</p>\n<p><strong>传奇抗性 Legendary Resistance（1/日）。</strong>你进行一次豁免检定失败时，可以选择将其改为豁免成功。</p>\n<p><strong>龙火 Dragon Fire。</strong>若你对生物或可燃物造成火焰伤害，目标会被点燃。在其每回合开始时，受到5([[/r 1d10]])点火焰伤害。 在被点燃目标触及范围内的生物可以使用一个动作将火焰扑灭。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"RoT","quantity":1,"weight":null,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"clothing","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G3qVbea14Vb3Is7f","name":"神风符文之帜 Pennant of the Vind Rune","type":"equipment","img":"icons/sundries/flags/banner-worn-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这面丝质的蓝色的三角旗长五尺，它如同被风吹拂一样来回摆动。vind（风）符文显现在它的表面，看起来像极了一朵云。三角旗具有以下特性，这些特性只在此三角旗装备在你身上时才能生效。</p>\n<p><strong>风之脚步Wind Step</strong>。 以一个动作，你飞行至多20尺。如果你在飞行结束时并未落地，除非你有另一种保持身处空中的方法，否则你会坠落。</p>\n<p><strong>舒适之风Comforting Wind</strong>。 你不会窒息。</p>\n<p><strong>风之掌控Wind's Grasp</strong>。 当你坠落时，你可以以一个反应使你自己避免此次坠落伤害。一旦你使用了这个特性，直到完成一次短休息或长休息之前，都无法再次使用，</p>\n<p><strong>风行者Wind Walker</strong>。 当你同调此符文时，你可以以一个附赠动作施展@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.GNvrHluGdgqD06wZ]{浮空术 Levitate}法术。一旦你使用了这个特性，直到完成一次短休息或长休息之前，都无法再次使用，</p>\n<p><strong>神风之赠礼Gift of Wind</strong>。 通过用你的手指在一件非魔法物品——一套盔甲、一双靴子或一件斗篷上描摹vind符文，你可以将三角旗的魔法转移到上面。转移需要花费8小时时间，并且需要两件物品在此期间互相间隔在5尺之内。在这8小时结束时，三角旗会被摧毁，并且银色的符文会出现在你所选择的物品上，这会使得该物品获得一项基于其形态的增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>盔甲Armo</strong>。 该盔甲现在成为一件非普通的魔法物品，需要同调。当你穿戴此盔甲时，你的移动速度提升5尺，并且如果该盔甲通常会使你在隐匿检定中具有劣势，它不再会如此。</li>\n<li><strong>靴子/斗篷 Boots/Cloak</strong>。 这双靴子或这间斗篷现在成为一件珍稀的魔法物品，需要同调。当你穿戴此物品时，你可以在自己的每个回合中将至多20尺的移动力转换为飞行。如果你在飞行结束时并未着陆落地，除非你有另一种保持空中飞行身处空中的方法，否则你会坠落。你也可以以该物品施展一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.NYTOuhtKx54qRDCT]{羽落术 Feather Fall}法术，并且当你完成一次短休息或长休息后，你恢复该能力。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SKT","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G8ol3vC7ZfIQxxYD","name":"地狱火匕首 Hellfire Dagger","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/dagger.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"dagger","properties":{"fin":true,"lgt":true,"thr":true,"amm":false,"hvy":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lod":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"two":false,"ver":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GJTg1TvIbQqEq3O9","name":"水之毁灭法球 Devastation Orb of Water","type":"consumable","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/grenade-round.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>毁灭法球是一种元素炸弹，可以在元素节点上通过使用邪恶元素武器进行仪式来制造。创建的法球类型取决于制造所使用的节点。例如，一个气元素节点会产生一个气之毁灭法球。这个仪式需要1个小时完成，需要2000gp的特殊材料，这些成分将会被消耗掉。</p>\n<p>毁灭法球直径12寸，重10磅，外壳坚固。这个球体在诞生后[[/r 1d100]]小时将会爆炸，释放出它所包含的元素能量。这个球体没有任何迹象显示它还需要多久才会爆炸。诸如@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.tyshE8ZcV1Xniej3]{鉴定术 Identify}和@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.0An7Gb3wSSffcHhV]{预言术 Divination}之类的法术可以用来确定球体爆炸的时间。一个球体有10点AC，15点生命值，对毒素和心灵伤害有免疫。降低到0点生命值会导致法球立刻爆炸。</p>\n<p>好在，可以制作一个特殊的容器来存放一个毁灭法球，以此防止它一言不合就爆炸。容器必须刻有球体相反元素的符号。例如，一个刻有大地符号的盒子可以用来封存一个气之毁灭法球。在容器中，球体会缓缓旋转。如果在本应引爆的时间之后将其从容器中取出，则法球会在[[/r 1d6]]轮之后爆炸，除非将其放回容器。</p>\n<p>无论法球的类型如何，它的作用范围都是一个半径为1里的球型区域。区域的中心是法球所在位置。一次使用后球体会被摧毁。</p>\n<p><strong>激雨法球Water Orb</strong>。当这个法球爆炸时，它会产生持续24小时的暴雨。在有效区域内，适用《地下城主指南》第5章中详细介绍的强降雨规则。如果有大量的雨水滞留在该地区，会在[[/r 2d10]]小时的大雨后导致洪水泛滥，洪水超过河岸10尺，淹没周围地区。此后，洪水以每轮100尺的速度向前推进，以河道水体为起点，直到到达影响区域的边缘：抵达该位置后，水向低处流动（可能会退回到它的源头）。轻型建筑倒塌并被冲走。任何位于洪水的路径上的大型或更小的生物都将被冲走。洪水毁坏庄稼，并可能引发泥石流，效果取决于地形。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PotA","quantity":1,"weight":10,"price":2000,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":24,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"mi","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"2d12","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"ammo"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GPoLsP9xlt2DK2zZ","name":"绿龙面具 Green Dragon Mask","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/mask-horned-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这个斑驳的绿色面具顶部有褶边纹饰，下巴处有皮革般的带刺金属板。面具会调整自身尺寸以便其同调者着装。你与之同调并着装后，可以使用下列各属性。</p>\n<p><strong>伤害吸收 Damage Absorption。</strong> 你对毒素伤害拥有抗性， 如果你已经从另一来源拥有了毒素伤害的抗性，则你改为对毒素伤害免疫。若你此前已从另一来源获得了毒素伤害免疫，则你在受到毒素伤害时，可恢复其伤害量一半的生命值。</p>\n<p><strong>龙形威严 Draconic Majesty。</strong>你未着装护甲时，可以将自己的魅力加值加入你的护甲等级中。</p>\n<p><strong>龙息 Dragon Breath。</strong>若你有本身拥有需要休息充能的吐息武器，则该吐息改为充能 6。</p>\n<p><strong>龙之视界 Dragon Sight。</strong>你获得 60 尺的黑暗视觉，若你已拥有黑暗视觉，则其范围再增加 60 尺。你每日有一次机会， 可获得持续 5 分钟的 30 尺的盲视感官。</p>\n<p><strong>龙言 Dragon Tongue。</strong>你可以说和理解龙语。你对黑龙进行的所有魅力检定都具有优势。</p>\n<p><strong>传奇抗性 Legendary Resistance（1/日）。</strong>你进行一次豁免检定失败时，可以选择将其改为豁免成功。</p>\n<p><strong>水下呼吸 Water Breathing。</strong>你可以在水下呼吸。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"RoT","quantity":1,"weight":null,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"clothing","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
