{"_id":"GahRGLPrbBkM9DMP","name":"地狱火刺剑 Hellfire Rapier","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/sword-short.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":2,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8 + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"rapier","properties":{"fin":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GfUulhUzjEKtTs2G","name":"命运的十二面体 Dodecahedron of Doom","type":"equipment","img":"icons/sundries/gaming/dice-pair-white-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>这个有着 12 个金属面的骰子，其五边形的侧面有 12 寸宽，刻有数 字 1-12。十二面体装有奥术发条装置，一旦投出骰子就会发出呼呼和滴滴的声音。</p>\n<p>作为一个动作，这个十二面体可以用力投出 60 尺高，落地滚动至少 10 尺静止后，将触发一个随机的魔法效果。如果效果需要一个目标但有效距离内没有合适的目标，那什么也不会发生。十二面体施放法术不需要任何材料。投掷一次[[/r d12]] 并根据下面的表格确定效果：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><strong>[[/r D12]]</strong></th>\n<th><strong>效果</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1-2</td>\n<td>十二面体爆炸并且损坏。在爆炸范围 20 尺内的每个生物需要做一个 DC13 的敏捷检定，失败受到 40 ([[/r 9D8]])点力场伤害，成功的话伤害减半。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3-4</td>\n<td>十二面体为自己点亮一盏灯。这个效果持续到下 一个生物触碰骰子。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5-6</td>\n<td>十二面体施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.tJzKo2vpEhXZfuJO]{冷冻射线 Ray of Frost}(命中+5)，随机攻击 60 尺 内 1 个没有处在完全遮蔽状态下的生物。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7-8</td>\n<td>十二面体对下一个触碰它的生物施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.0kzjiCnyoMHwijsp]{电爪 Shocking Grasp}(命中 +5)。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9-10</td>\n<td>十二面体对自己施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.UyQ9nYcQlFdEbmeV]{黑暗术 Darkness}，效果持续 10 分钟。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11-12</td>\n<td>下一个触碰十二面体的生物获得[[/r 1D10]]的临时生命，持续 1 小时。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDMM","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d12","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem"