{"_id":"NNIDwIzjrammI0TR","name":"法术宝石 Spell Gem","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/treasure/crown-blue-gold.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（部分需同调）</em></p>\n<p>一枚法术宝石可以储存一发任意等级职业相应环阶的法术。你将在得知宝石的属性后知晓其内含法术的具体状况。持握宝石时，若你知晓其内的法术且该法术在你的职业法术列表中，则你可以用一个动作施展该法术。以该方式施展法术时无需与宝石同调也不需要任何法术成分。施法过后，宝石中的法术也随之消散。</p>\n<p>如果宝石里的高环阶法术超过了你当前可施展法术环阶，则你需要以你的施法关键属性进行一次额外的检定，以判断本次施法是否成功。其DC 为10＋该法术的环阶。检定失败时，该法术失效且宝石中的法术也随之消散。</p>\n<p>不同类型的法术宝石 其能够存储法术的最大环阶也各不相同。宝石与法术环阶相关的稀有度和储存法术其豁免DC 与攻击加值，具体如“法术宝石”表所示。</p>\n<p>与宝石同调后，你可以在宝石内未有法术时将一发法术注入其中。此时，你需要手握空的宝石并正常施展一次该法术，然后法术便会注入宝石中而不是正常生效。法术的施法时间必须是 1 动作或不低于 1 分钟时间，且其法术环阶必须不高于宝石的上限。如果该法术是防护系且需要耗材，则你也需要满足相应需求，不过只需一半材料就能完成该作业。</p>\n<p>被注入法术后，同一枚宝石必须在下次黎明过后才能再次向其注入法术。</p>\n<p>这些法术宝石由地底侏儒制作而成，不过他们并不愿意跟别人分享这种秘密工艺。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"5\"><strong>法术宝石</strong></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><strong> 最大法术环价 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 宝石 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 稀有度 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 豁免DC </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 攻击加值 </strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>戏法</td>\n<td>黑曜石Obsidian</td>\n<td>非普通</td>\n<td>13</td>\n<td>+5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1环</td>\n<td>天青石Lapis lazuli</td>\n<td>非普通</td>\n<td>13</td>\n<td>+5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2环</td>\n<td>石英Quartz</td>\n<td>珍稀</td>\n<td>13</td>\n<td>+5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3环</td>\n<td>血石Bloodstone</td>\n<td>珍稀</td>\n<td>15</td>\n<td>+7</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4环</td>\n<td>琥珀Amber</td>\n<td>极珍稀</td>\n<td>15</td>\n<td>+9</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5环</td>\n<td>翡翠Jade</td>\n<td>极珍稀</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>+9</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6环</td>\n<td>黄玉Topaz</td>\n<td>极珍稀</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>+10</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7环</td>\n<td>星彩红宝石Star ruby</td>\n<td>传说</td>\n<td>18</td>\n<td>+10</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8环</td>\n<td>红宝石Ruby</td>\n<td>传说</td>\n<td>18</td>\n<td>+10</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9环</td>\n<td>钻石Diamond</td>\n<td>传说</td>\n<td>19</td>\n<td>+11</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"OoTA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"NSL9ehNkYKnJrgsk","name":"反噬之矛 Spear of Backbiting","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/spear-flared-wrapped.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>你用该魔法武器发动的攻击检定和伤害掷骰具 +2 加值。用其进行投掷时，它的常规和最大射程都增加 30 尺，且命中后增加一枚额外的伤害骰。投掷完成后，它无论是否命中都会立即飞回你手中。</p>\n<p><strong>诅咒Curse</strong>。与这支受诅咒武器同调的生物将受到其诅咒影响。只要诅咒还在生效，你总是会把它放在触手可及的地方，不愿与它分开。此外，你使用除它之外的任何武器发动攻击检定时具有劣势。</p>\n<p>以该武器发动攻击检定骰出 1 时，它会突然弯曲或飞转攻击你的后背。进行一次带优势的攻击检定，对抗你自身AC。若命中，则你受到伤害，如同你用它捅了自己。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TftYP","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":true,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":50,"long":90,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"+2","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6+2+@mod","piercing"]],"versatile":"1d8+2+@mod"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"spear","properties":{"thr":true,"ver":true,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ret":true,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":true,"attuned":true,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"NSwsbGsVu1iIMC9e","name":"盾牌符文之锭 Ingot of the Skold Rune","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/metal/ingot-stamped-steel.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这奇物看起来是一块朴素的铁矿石锭，大约一尺长，几寸宽。检查其表面可以看见skold（盾牌）符文暗淡的银色轮廓。铸块具有以下特性，这些特性只在此铸块装备在你身上时才能生效。</p>\n<p><strong>符文之盾Runic Shield</strong>。 你在AC上获得+1加值。</p>\n<p><strong>盾之连结Shield Bond</strong>。 以一个附赠动作，选择一个30尺内你所能看到的除你以外生物。直到你的下一回合结束，目标所受到的伤害将会减少至1，但是你会受到以此方式防止的伤害的一半。你所承受的伤害无法以任何方式减少。一旦你使用了这个特性，直到完成一次短休息或长休息之前，都无法再次使用，</p>\n<p><strong>盾之守护Shield Ward</strong>。 通过用你的手指在一件非魔法物品——一把武器或一件盔甲上描摹skold符文，你可以将铸块的魔法转移到上面。转移需要花费8小时时间，并且需要两件物品在此期间互相间隔在5尺之内。在这8小时结束时，铸块会被摧毁，并且银色的符文会出现在你所选择的物品上，这会使得该物品获得一项基于其形态的增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>盾牌Shield</strong>。 该盾牌现在成为一件珍稀的魔法物品，需要同调。它的魔法使你在AC上获得+1加值，并且每当你进行一次长休之后、第一次受到将你的生命值降低至O的伤害时，你改为降低生命值至1点。要获得这种好处，你必须持有该盾牌。</li>\n<li><strong>武器Weapon</strong>。该武器现在成为一件非普通的魔法物品。当你持有它的时候，你在AC上获得+1加值。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SKT","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[{"_id":"Pat3fnPmzL3nQYvl","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.ac.bonus","mode":2,"value":"1"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/commodities/metal/ingot-stamped-steel.webp","label":"AC + 1","origin":"Item.NSwsbGsVu1iIMC9e","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OIP1RUpYd2tMVHd5","name":"领主套装 Lord's Ensemble","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/back/cloak-hooded-jewels-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物(需人形生物同调)</em></p>\n<p>深水城的蒙面领主们在会面时穿戴此套装，以保证各 自的身份无法被区分。该套装由三件物品——一个头盔、 一条项链、一件长袍——组成，但在同调时视为一件魔法物品。套装只在深水城及其下水道范围内生效，并且必须 三件同时穿戴。</p>\n<p><strong>领主桶盔。</strong>这顶桶盔覆盖你的头部，隐藏了你的面容。 眼睛位置的镂空使头盔隐藏你身份的同时不会影响你的视线。佩戴此头盔时，你的声音被魔法效果变得雌雄难辨。 同时，你免疫阅读你的思想、侦测你是否说谎、侦测你的 阵营、或是侦测你生物种类的魔法效果。只有在你同意时， 其他生物才能用心灵感应和你交流。</p>\n<p><strong>领主项链。</strong>此项链是深水城权力巅峰的象征。它的效果视同@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.B5EFD9923B73D410]{反侦护符 Amulet of Proof against Detection and Location}。</p>\n<p><strong>领主长袍。</strong>这件优雅的长袍效果视同@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.4FA94D53C10938CE]{自由行动戒指 Ring of Free Action}，并且制造出幻象让你看起来像是身高 6 英尺，外貌平平无奇，性别难辨的类人生物。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDH","quantity":1,"weight":null,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"clothing","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OKWMNtA2qDMV2Mzm","name":"地狱犬斗篷 Hell Hound Cloak","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/back/cloak-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这件黑色斗篷以地狱犬的兽皮制成。你可以用一个动作命令斗篷将你自身变成一头地狱犬，并维持至多1 小时。该变形的其他效应等同于@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.IXs3Neqbl8xaT3yk]{变形术 Polymorph}，只是你可以用一个附赠动作使自己恢复原形。</p>\n<p><strong>诅咒Curse</strong>。这件斗篷已被地狱犬的精髓诅咒，因而会逐步侵蚀其主人。只要诅咒还在生效，你总是会把斗篷放在触手可及的地方，且不愿与它分开。 <br />第六次使用斗篷后，你在随后每当再使用斗篷时都必须进行一次DC 15 的魅力豁免。豁免失败则变形将一直持续至被驱散或直至你的生命值降到0，且无法自主恢复原形。如果保持地狱犬形态的时间达到 6 小时，变形效应将被恒定，你也将失去自我。你的所有资料将被地狱犬的资料替代。此后，只有@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ewDH2w8w2yLSM021]{移除诅咒 Remove Curse}或类似法术才能让你找回自我并恢复通常状态。如果你保持该恒定状态的时间达到 6 日，则只有@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xjn6gjItpWpldE53]{祈愿术 Wish}才能解除该变形。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TftYP","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"cha","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"clothing","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OLBkG6gF7FVZ5xdS","name":"黎明使者 Dawnbringer","type":"weapon","img":"icons/magic/fire/beam-jet-stream-trails-orange.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需要一位非邪恶阵营生物同调）</em></p>\n<p>在幽暗地域中失落多年的黎明使者其本体是一把镶金的剑柄。抓握剑柄时，你可以用一个附赠动作从中展开或收起一道由光芒形成的剑刃。黎明使者具有@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.152FDAA04D28AF9E]{阳炎剑 Sun Blade} 的所有属性。</p>\n<p>持握这把武器时，你可以用一个动作以光刃触碰一个生物，以此对该生物施展一道@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.I1C2EQxwynPd7dOC]{次级复原术 Lesser Restoration}。该能力使用过后必须等到下次黎明才能再用。</p>\n<p><strong>智能Sentience</strong>。黎明使者是一把中立善良的智能武器，它拥有12 智力，15 感知和14 魅力，具有听觉和120 尺黑暗视觉。<br />这把剑可以听、说、读通用语，能够使用心灵感应交流。它的声音是一把和蔼的女声，且能够理解与之同调者知晓的所有语言。</p>\n<p><strong>个性Personality</strong>。由远古太阳崇拜者铸造的黎明使者，其存在是为了在黑暗中带来光明，以及与黑暗中的敌人作战。它对自己人和蔼可亲，对敌人却凶猛而残酷。<br />由于被遗落在黑暗中太久，黎明使者 现在有点惧怕黑暗和被遗弃。它希望自己的光刃一直展开以持续向黑暗区域散发光亮，并且强烈抗拒跟自己的持用者分开太远。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"OoTA","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"2","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8 + @mod +2","radiant"]],"versatile":"1d10 + @mod +2"},"formula":"1d8","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"longsword","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":true,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":true,"mgc":true,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OODrccSS2I54PQNN","name":"地狱火巨棒 Hellfire Greatclub","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/greatclub.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":10,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8 + @mod","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"greatclub","properties":{"two":true,"amm":false,"hvy":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"ver":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OTqJDdMcYVu7OMy3","name":"召唤冠恐鸟之羽 Feather of Diatryma Summoning","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/materials/feather-colored-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物(需同调)</em></p>\n<p>这枚闪闪发光的羽毛饰品是由冠恐鸟 diatryma 的羽 毛制造的。冠恐鸟是一种生活在幽暗地域的有着多彩羽毛但不能飞行的大型鸟类。如果你用一个动作说出命令词并将羽毛扔到你周围 5 英尺内一处大型的未占据区域，它会 变成一只活的冠恐鸟，持续 6 小时。当持续时间结束时、 或冠恐鸟生命值降低到 0 时、或你用一个动作触摸冠恐鸟并说出命令词时，它将变回羽毛形态。</p>\n<p>冠恐鸟变回羽毛形态后，它的魔法效果需要经过 7 天才能再次启动。</p>\n<p>冠恐鸟使用斧嘴鸟 axebeak 的数据，但它的喙啄攻击造成穿刺伤害而非挥砍伤害。它对你和你的同伴友善， 并且可以作为坐骑。它能理解你说的语言并且遵从你的口 头命令。如果你不发布任何命令，它只会自卫。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDH","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"命令词。"},"duration":{"value":6,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","autoDestroy":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Oxc4PdOTDd6Rt8fH","name":"岩石符文之球 Orb of the Stein Rune","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/stone/stone-white-quartz-ball.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这个花岗岩球体大约与有一个成年人类的拳头大小。stein（岩石）符文以水晶状纹理的形式出现在它的表面。该球体具有以下特性，这些特性只在此球体装备在你身上时才能生效。</p>\n<p><strong>顽强Indomitable Stand</strong>。 以一个动作，你可以引导球体的魔法来维持住你的阵脚。在接下来的一分钟或直到你进行任何移动之前，你在所有抵抗迫使你移动效果的检定和豁免上具有优势。此外，任何移动到距离你10尺内的敌人必须通过DC12的力量豁免，否则不能在此回合中移动更多的距离。</p>\n<p><strong>岩石之魂Stone Soul</strong>。 你不会被石化。</p>\n<p><strong>土之脚步Earthen Step</strong>。 你可以以一个附赠动作施展@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.pJ6hE8Vab5Ypuqm4]{融身入石 Meld into Stone}法术。一旦你使用了这个特性，直到完成一次短休息或长休息之前，都无法再次使用，</p>\n<p><strong>岩石之赠礼Gift of Stone</strong>。 通过用你的手指在一件非魔法物品——一面盾牌或一双靴子上描摹stein符文，你可以将球体的魔法转移到上面。转移需要花费8小时时间，并且需要两件物品在此期间互相间隔在5尺之内。在这8小时结束时，球体会被摧毁，并且银色的符文会出现在你所选择的物品上，这会使得该物品获得一项基于其形态的增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>盾牌Shield</strong>。 该盾牌现在成为一件珍稀的魔法物品，需要同调。当你使用它时，你对所有远程武器攻击所造成的伤害具有抗性。</li>\n<li><strong>靴子Boots</strong>。 这双靴子现在成为一件非普通的魔法物品，需要同调。当你穿上靴子时候，你在力量豁免上获得优势，并且你可以使用你的反应动作来避免被击倒在地。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SKT","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":12,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"trinket"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"P1Xb8FXpKqfWh0zh","name":"法术宝石（星彩红宝石）Spell Gem (Star ruby)","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-faceted-radiant-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（部分需同调）</em></p>\n<p>一枚法术宝石可以储存一发任意等级职业相应环阶的法术。你将在得知宝石的属性后知晓其内含法术的具体状况。持握宝石时，若你知晓其内的法术且该法术在你的职业法术列表中，则你可以用一个动作施展该法术。以该方式施展法术时无需与宝石同调也不需要任何法术成分。施法过后，宝石中的法术也随之消散。</p>\n<p>如果宝石里的高环阶法术超过了你当前可施展法术环阶，则你需要以你的施法关键属性进行一次额外的检定，以判断本次施法是否成功。其DC 为10＋该法术的环阶。检定失败时，该法术失效且宝石中的法术也随之消散。</p>\n<p>不同类型的法术宝石 其能够存储法术的最大环阶也各不相同。宝石与法术环阶相关的稀有度和储存法术其豁免DC 与攻击加值，具体如“法术宝石”表所示。</p>\n<p>与宝石同调后，你可以在宝石内未有法术时将一发法术注入其中。此时，你需要手握空的宝石并正常施展一次该法术，然后法术便会注入宝石中而不是正常生效。法术的施法时间必须是 1 动作或不低于 1 分钟时间，且其法术环阶必须不高于宝石的上限。如果该法术是防护系且需要耗材，则你也需要满足相应需求，不过只需一半材料就能完成该作业。</p>\n<p>被注入法术后，同一枚宝石必须在下次黎明过后才能再次向其注入法术。</p>\n<p>这些法术宝石由地底侏儒制作而成，不过他们并不愿意跟别人分享这种秘密工艺。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"5\"><strong>法术宝石</strong></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><strong> 最大法术环价 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 宝石 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 稀有度 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 豁免DC </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 攻击加值 </strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>7环</td>\n<td>星彩红宝石Star ruby</td>\n<td>传说</td>\n<td>18</td>\n<td>+10</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"OoTA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"P29VSSsb87SH7ylY","name":"地狱火短剑 Hellfire Shortsword","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/sword-short.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":2,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6 + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"shortsword","properties":{"fin":true,"lgt":true,"amm":false,"hvy":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lod":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Pgp6qNA8rMQayQsZ","name":"野兽面具 Mask of the Beast","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/mask-carved-gargoyle-grey.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>这个木制的面具被雕刻成仿冒野兽的外观，拥有三次充能。带着面具时，你可以以一个动作消耗一次充能使用面具释放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.t09Fa4kTkkIgMoDu]{化兽为友 Animal Friendship}。这一面具会在黎明时重新获得所有被使用的充能。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"3","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PzWxPt32DCS0n83E","name":"砍伐者 Hew","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-broad-crescent-gray.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>这是一把一把矮人工艺制作的生锈战斧。其斧头上刻着矮人语的符文“砍伐者 Hew”，而其锈迹只是一种视觉误导。</p>\n</div>\n<p>砍伐者是一把+1 战斧 Battleaxe，当其持用者用它攻击植物生物或木制物件时，其造成的伤害直接取满。而带着这把斧头穿越森林 的人总会感到一阵有点不自在。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LMoP","quantity":1,"weight":4,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"+1","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+1+@mod","slashing"]],"versatile":"1d10+1+@mod"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"battleaxe","properties":{"ver":true,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
