{"_id":"Ty1rghIhaQWuxNTj","name":"鸣锣宝珠 Orb of Gonging","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/tech/bearing-steel-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>这个物品直径 5 寸、 重 5 磅，是呈中空的球形。外壳是由锯齿状的青铜环组成， 这些环可以转动，使锯齿的缺口连成一条线。对齐缺口需要花费一个动作，这将导致球体持续发出巨大的锣声， 直到锯齿不再对齐才会停止。这些声音间隔 6 秒，能够传到 600 尺范围内。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDMM","quantity":1,"weight":5,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":600,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"UK0VLrXv2MKxAG3v","name":"飞匕护腕 Bracer of Flying Daggers","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/wrist/bracer-belted-leather-steel.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物(需同调)</em></p>\n<p>这双护腕看起来捆了若干小匕首。你可以用一个动作拔出至多两把魔法匕首并即刻投出。为每把匕首分别进行一次远程攻击检定。若你没有立即扔出匕首，它们将消失不见。无论命中与否，匕首都会在攻击之后消失。护腕中可以拔出的匕首数量是无限的。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDH","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"dex","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4+@mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
