{"_id":"UMFYg9Fszcz1LbSw","name":"书签 Bookmark","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-serrated-black.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这柄+3的匕首属于Artus Cimber。当你抽出这柄匕首时，你可以以一个奖励动作发动以下特性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>让匕首柄末嵌入的蓝色宝石发出二十尺的明亮光线以及范围外二十尺的昏暗光线，或是让宝石暗下去。</li>\n<li>将匕首变成一个当它放在你的掌心时指向北方的指南针</li>\n<li>从匕首释放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.u86hMx0ODfccAtu8]{任意门 Dimension Door}。一旦被使用，这一特性在下一次黎明前无法使用</li>\n<li>从匕首施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.RpBbOYseLZCFXaFY]{强迫术 Compulsion}（豁免DC15）。这一法术效应的范围增加到90尺，但只能对着野兽类的支柱使用。这一效应一旦施放，下次黎明前无法使用。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"mgc":false,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
