{"_id":"UauDwrxVMh7Hzepk","name":"心灵控制药水（野兽）Potion of Mind Control (beast)","type":"consumable","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-conical-corked-purple.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>饮用心灵控制药水后，你可以在自己下个回合结束前对某一指定生物施展支配法术（豁免DC 15）。如果你不施展该法术，则该药水的效应将浪费掉。</p>\n<p>心灵控制药水（野兽）能产生@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xaSXewdCx3aWtczk]{支配野兽 Dominate Beast}。如果目标的首次豁免失败，其效应将持续 1 小时，且你无须保持专注。在效应持续期间，被魅惑生物再次进行破除该效应的豁免检定时都将承受劣势。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TftYP","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"abil","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"potion","attuned":false,"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"VNRou693ZhLxqGoa","name":"炼狱谜盒 Infernal Puzzle Box","type":"equipment","img":"icons/containers/chest/chest-reinforced-box-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>炼狱谜盒是一个边长5到6寸的立方体形容器，由九狱中的材料制成的密闭、连锁的部件组成。这些盒子大多由炼狱铁制成，但也有一些是用骨头或角雕成的。炼狱谜盒是用来保护魔鬼和凡人之间签订的魔鬼合同，即使这些合同的条款已经履行。一个空的炼狱谜盒重3磅，不管它是用什么材料做的。</p>\n<p>当一个小到可以装进炼狱谜盒的物体被放入其中时，容器就会神奇地封住这个物体，并且没有任何魔法可以强行打开盒子。密封的盒子也会对所有类型的伤害免疫。每一个炼狱谜盒都是用一种独特的方法来打开的。解决这个谜题的诀窍总是平凡的，而不是魔法的。一旦一个生物想出了打开一个炼狱谜盒所需的技巧或步骤序列，该生物就可以以一个动作打开炼狱谜盒，并且能够获得炼狱谜盒的内容。</p>\n<p>一个生物如果花费1小时拿着一个炼狱谜盒并尝试打开它，就可以进行一次DC 30的智力(调查)检定。如果检定成功，该生物就能够知道打开盒子所需的技巧或步骤。如果检定失败5次或以上，该生物必须进行一次DC 18的感知豁免检定，豁免失败则将受到42([[/r 12d6]])点心灵伤害，成功则伤害减半。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"hour","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["12d6","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"int","dc":30,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
