{"_id":"VkmaUGI5Q1CkB5xH","name":"夺心魔头骨 Mind Flayer Skull","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/bones/skull-monster-beige.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>使用侦测魔法可以发现幻术系魔法灵光环绕 在这个夺心魔头骨上，使用鉴定术或类似的法术能够鉴别出头骨的魔法属性。持有头骨的生物(以及其装备或者携带的物品)，对于夺心魔来说是隐形的。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDMM","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"VsC4QKM8Y2MdvtSV","name":"雷鸣权杖 Blast Scepter","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-round-ornate-purple.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>它可以用作奥术法器。</p>\n<p>任何与雷鸣权杖同调的人都能获得对火焰和闪电伤害的抗性，并且可以使用它作为 4 环法术(豁免 DC 16)施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.8GM6YBgYFPIcFXKg]{雷鸣波 Thunderwave}而不会消耗法术位。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDMM","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + @mod","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"club","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"mgc":false,"lgt":true,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false},"effects":[{"_id":"HbyDeOn5MhGjvkMn","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"fire"},{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"lightning"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-round-ornate-purple.webp","label":"火焰、闪电抗性 +","origin":"Item.VsC4QKM8Y2MdvtSV","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"VvGv5jAVsWZSAOht","name":"范拉克的秘银盔甲 Vanrak's Mithral Shirt","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-banded-steel-grey.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>秘银是一种轻盈柔韧的金属。秘银链甲衫或胸甲可以穿在普通衣物下面。某种盔甲可能会造成穿着者敏捷（隐秘）检定上的劣势，或是对穿着者的力量属性有要求，但它的秘银版本没有这些特性。</p>\n<p>范拉克·星月的远古秘银盔甲（链甲衫）赋予穿着者 60 尺黑暗视觉。如果某个玩家在范拉克深渊中穿上这套盔甲，附近会出现两个幽影刺客并攻击该玩家。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDMM","quantity":1,"weight":20,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":13,"type":"medium","dex":2},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"chainshirt","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"effects":[{"_id":"LcRju1b6TMBopC17","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.senses.darkvision","mode":2,"value":"60"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-banded-steel-grey.webp","label":"+ 60 ft. 黑暗视觉","origin":"Item.VvGv5jAVsWZSAOht","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"WCrG2KV3mW3lupkx","name":"法术宝石（翡翠）Spell Gem (Jade)","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-rough-drop-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（部分需同调）</em></p>\n<p>一枚法术宝石可以储存一发任意等级职业相应环阶的法术。你将在得知宝石的属性后知晓其内含法术的具体状况。持握宝石时，若你知晓其内的法术且该法术在你的职业法术列表中，则你可以用一个动作施展该法术。以该方式施展法术时无需与宝石同调也不需要任何法术成分。施法过后，宝石中的法术也随之消散。</p>\n<p>如果宝石里的高环阶法术超过了你当前可施展法术环阶，则你需要以你的施法关键属性进行一次额外的检定，以判断本次施法是否成功。其DC 为10＋该法术的环阶。检定失败时，该法术失效且宝石中的法术也随之消散。</p>\n<p>不同类型的法术宝石 其能够存储法术的最大环阶也各不相同。宝石与法术环阶相关的稀有度和储存法术其豁免DC 与攻击加值，具体如“法术宝石”表所示。</p>\n<p>与宝石同调后，你可以在宝石内未有法术时将一发法术注入其中。此时，你需要手握空的宝石并正常施展一次该法术，然后法术便会注入宝石中而不是正常生效。法术的施法时间必须是 1 动作或不低于 1 分钟时间，且其法术环阶必须不高于宝石的上限。如果该法术是防护系且需要耗材，则你也需要满足相应需求，不过只需一半材料就能完成该作业。</p>\n<p>被注入法术后，同一枚宝石必须在下次黎明过后才能再次向其注入法术。</p>\n<p>这些法术宝石由地底侏儒制作而成，不过他们并不愿意跟别人分享这种秘密工艺。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"5\"><strong>法术宝石</strong></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><strong> 最大法术环价 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 宝石 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 稀有度 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 豁免DC </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 攻击加值 </strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>5环</td>\n<td>翡翠Jade</td>\n<td>极珍稀</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>+9</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"OoTA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"WEffkUaz8JmUHzrh","name":"星尘团 Vial of Stardust","type":"consumable","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-corked-empty.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这些星尘团在@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.cGO3m3Xu4mtPegr4]{侦测魔法 Detect Magic}下散发出幻术系的魔法灵光。一个@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.tyshE8ZcV1Xniej3]{鉴定术 Identify}或类似的魔法揭示了尘埃有一种独特的魔法属性。任何将尘土撒向自身的生物都可以获得一次以一个动作施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.40z4HpFVUux7h03S]{托梦术 Dream}（DC 15），无需任何材料。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDMM","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":"","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":15,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"potion"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"XLzKJoOVUhEjeH2u","name":"回忆烟斗 Pipe of Remembrance","type":"equipment","img":"icons/sundries/misc/pipe-elegant.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>这支狭长精致的木制烟管配有一个由光滑河石制成的斗部。当烟斗被点燃时，它呼出的烟雾不会散去，而是在持有者周围萦绕徘徊。在10分钟后，烟雾的形态变化并在五分钟里重现出持有者最为深刻和英勇的事迹。当这一栩栩如生的表演结束时，烟雾随之消散。</p>\n<p>该烟斗直到第二日黎明无法被以这种方式再次使用。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GoS","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"minute","cost":10,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":5,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Xpq8sIRNRY4XZ2Vs","name":"法术宝石（黄玉）Spell Gem (Topaz)","type":"consumable","img":"icons/commodities/gems/gem-rough-rectangular-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（部分需同调）</em></p>\n<p>一枚法术宝石可以储存一发任意等级职业相应环阶的法术。你将在得知宝石的属性后知晓其内含法术的具体状况。持握宝石时，若你知晓其内的法术且该法术在你的职业法术列表中，则你可以用一个动作施展该法术。以该方式施展法术时无需与宝石同调也不需要任何法术成分。施法过后，宝石中的法术也随之消散。</p>\n<p>如果宝石里的高环阶法术超过了你当前可施展法术环阶，则你需要以你的施法关键属性进行一次额外的检定，以判断本次施法是否成功。其DC 为10＋该法术的环阶。检定失败时，该法术失效且宝石中的法术也随之消散。</p>\n<p>不同类型的法术宝石 其能够存储法术的最大环阶也各不相同。宝石与法术环阶相关的稀有度和储存法术其豁免DC 与攻击加值，具体如“法术宝石”表所示。</p>\n<p>与宝石同调后，你可以在宝石内未有法术时将一发法术注入其中。此时，你需要手握空的宝石并正常施展一次该法术，然后法术便会注入宝石中而不是正常生效。法术的施法时间必须是 1 动作或不低于 1 分钟时间，且其法术环阶必须不高于宝石的上限。如果该法术是防护系且需要耗材，则你也需要满足相应需求，不过只需一半材料就能完成该作业。</p>\n<p>被注入法术后，同一枚宝石必须在下次黎明过后才能再次向其注入法术。</p>\n<p>这些法术宝石由地底侏儒制作而成，不过他们并不愿意跟别人分享这种秘密工艺。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"5\"><strong>法术宝石</strong></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th><strong> 最大法术环价 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 宝石 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 稀有度 </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 豁免DC </strong></th>\n<th><strong> 攻击加值 </strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>6环</td>\n<td>黄玉Topaz</td>\n<td>极珍稀</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>+10</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"OoTA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"trinket"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Xu5309APnkDEgKsz","name":"渔夫的喜悦之钩 Hook of Fisher's Delight","type":"equipment","img":"icons/commodities/metal/fragments-steel-barbed.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>奇物</p>\n<p>这个小小的银色鱼钩上附有一根金色小羽毛。为使其产生效果，你必须将它系在鱼线的末端并沉入足够大的水域中（至少10立方尺）。每当你不间断地将其沉入水中1小时，骰一次[[/r d6]]。骰值为6时，一条6寸长的魔法鱼耷拉在鱼钩尾部。被变出的鱼的颜色和效应由下表的掷骰决定。一旦该鱼钩变出了鱼，直到第二天黎明时，它都不能再如此做。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><strong> [[/r d20]]</strong></th>\n<th><strong>鱼的颜色</strong></th>\n<th><strong>魔法效应</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1~10</td>\n<td>绿色，带有铜色条纹</td>\n<td>这条美味的鱼可以为吃掉它的生物满足一整天的营养需求。若在被抓到24小时后仍未被食用，这条鱼将失去该效应并腐烂。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11~14</td>\n<td>黄色，带有黑色条纹</td>\n<td>当被从鱼钩上取下后，这条难吃的鱼可以用来投掷。指定120尺内投掷者能看见的一个生物，该生物必须进行一次DC15的力量豁免。豁免失败者将被击倒地。随后这条鱼消失。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>15~18</td>\n<td>蓝色，带有白色条纹</td>\n<td>当被从鱼钩上释放后，这条鱼将长出翅膀跟着你自由地舞动，并用水族语歌唱一曲优美的旋律。[[/r 2d4]]小时后或生命值降为0时，它将消失。这条鱼使用食人鱼Quipper的数值，但它可以在空气中呼吸且拥有30尺的飞行速度。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>19~20</td>\n<td>金色，带有银色条纹</td>\n<td>这条美味的鱼可以为吃掉它的生物满足一整天的营养需求，并为该生物提供[[/r 2d10]]临时生命。若在被抓到24小时后仍未被食用，这条鱼将失去该效应并腐烂。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"IDRotF","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"hour","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YjnIEV6KYPPWZOOK","name":"召唤泰拉斯奎巨兽卷轴 Scroll of Tarrasque Summoning","type":"consumable","img":"icons/sundries/scrolls/scroll-bound-skull-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>以一个动作阅读这张卷轴将会令泰拉斯奎巨兽 Tarrasque 显现在你1里范围内可见的一处未被占据的空间。它对除它自身以外的所有生物都抱有敌意，且在生命值降至0时消失。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"IDRotF","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"scroll","attuned":false,"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Ykyd1sSzavj1b12b","name":"地狱火链枷 Hellfire Flail","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/morningstar.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":2,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+@mod","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"flail","properties":{"value":"","amm":false,"hvy":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YvvAzW6sB5qFt1tj","name":"追踪提灯 Lantern of Tracking","type":"equipment","img":"icons/sundries/lights/lantern-bullseye-signal-copper.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>这个附有灯罩的提灯在点燃后每6小时消耗1品脱的灯油。它提供30尺的明亮光照以及其外30尺的微光光照。</p>\n<p>每个追踪提灯都被设计成用来发现某种生物的踪迹，具体类型由下表的掷骰决定。追踪的生物类型一旦被确定便不能再更改。当提灯距符合其类型的生物300尺以内时，它的火焰将变为亮绿色。不过，该提灯并不能精确定位那些生物的位置。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><strong>[[/r d10]]</strong></th>\n<th><strong>生物类型</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>异怪</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>天界生物</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>构装生物</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>龙类</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>元素生物</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>精类</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>邪魔</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>巨人</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>怪兽</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>不死生物</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"IDRotF","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":6,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":300,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"material","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YxWvXzkQbFL4HuyS","name":"地狱火战镐 Hellfire War Pick","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/pick.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":2,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8 + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"warpick","properties":{"value":"","amm":false,"hvy":false,"fin":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"lod":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false,"attributes":{"spelldc":10}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Z4i06Y9DJRMFExau","name":"压力胶囊 Pressure Capsule","type":"consumable","img":"icons/consumables/food/candy-taffy-blue-white.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>这个小小的胶囊由蜜蜡与沙子以及多种具有魔力的水生植物制成。一个吃下压力胶囊的生物能够无视在100尺之下更深的水中游泳的效应。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GoS","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"food"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Z7wIZcd6Ku5Gvk8D","name":"阿弗纳斯之刃 Blade of Avernus","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/greatsword-crossguard-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在扎瑞尔之剑被摧毁后的某个时刻，扎瑞尔给了她的仆人（包括那些扮演过此的角色）为她锻造一把新剑的任务。这项企图包括的目标如下：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果贝尔还在为扎瑞尔服务，她会请求他去锻造刀锋。否则，她的仆人必须在宇宙中找到一个相当的武器铁匠，比如火元素位面黄铜城的一名火巨灵。</li>\n<li>扎瑞尔至少需要十磅的金属或材料来制造剑的刀刃。精金或者是提亚马特的爪子都行。</li>\n<li>为了赋予剑力量，新锻造的武器必须在天界生物、恶魔领主和魔鬼大公的血液中淬火。扎瑞尔可以供应自己的血，但她的仆人必须收集另外两份。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>扎瑞尔将这个新的神器命名为阿弗纳斯之刃。这把长剑是一个需要同调的神器，它具有以下属性：</p>\n<p><strong>魔法武器 Magic Weapons</strong>。阿弗纳斯之刃是一把魔法武器，有@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.8BC379E202BC7596]{斩首长剑 Vorpal Longsword}的效果。</p>\n<p><strong>随机属性 Random Properties</strong>。剑具有以下随机确定的属性，如《城主指南》第7章所述：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>2项弱效增益属性</li>\n<li>1项强效增益属性</li>\n<li>1项强效减益属性，当剑与大魔鬼同调时会被压制</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>阿弗纳斯的统治者 Ruler of Avernus</strong>。以一个动作，你可以把这把剑指向一个离你60尺以内的魔鬼。魔鬼必须成功通过一个DC22的魅力豁免检定，否则被你魅惑1小时。以这种方式被魅惑的话魔鬼会全力执行你的命令。如果你命令魔鬼去做一些它认为是自杀的事，效果便会结束，你也无法再用这把剑的力量来对付这个魔鬼。</p>\n<p><strong>炼狱回返 Infernal Recall</strong>。以一个动作，你可以用这把剑来释放一个@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.saFwXc26RtQaVLWN]{回返真言 Word of Recall}。被这个法术传送的生物出现在当前阿弗纳斯统治者30尺范围内的一个未被占据的地方，或者你指定的一个避难所，如果你统治了阿弗纳斯的话。</p>\n<p><strong>摧毁这把剑 Destroying the Sword</strong>。把剑扔进冥河或者在铸造它的熔炉中将其熔化都可以摧毁它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"artifact","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"+3","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+3+@mod","slashing"]],"versatile":"1d10+3+@mod"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"longsword","properties":{"ver":true,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":true,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZBtbp0XRbbn1V113","name":"龙后面具 Mask of the Dragon Queen","type":"equipment","img":"icons/equipment/head/helm-barbute-evil-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>每一个单独的巨龙面具都如同他们名字中的巨龙一样。当两个 或更多的巨龙面具组装在一起时，它们会变成龙后面具。每个面具 缩小成为彩色龙的模型头部，似乎咆哮着对龙后的忠诚。所有面具聚集在一起，在佩戴者的头上呈冠状。 在五个面具下面，一个新的面具自动塑形，赋予佩戴者一个覆盖面部、颈部和肩部的新龙形面貌。</p>\n<p>当你同调并戴上这个面具时，你可以选择拥有其中一个面具的全部能力。你可以用另一次同调更改为另一个面具的全部能力。除此之外，你能从 5 个龙面具中获得所有的伤害吸收能力，同时你总共获得 5 次传奇抗性。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.70Fdi3lETOkPVWv8]{黑龙面具 Black Dragon Mask}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.LqinUSfQ2xIRD6VP]{蓝龙面具 Blue Dragon Mask}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.GPoLsP9xlt2DK2zZ]{绿龙面具 Green Dragon Mask}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.FebP0mOo7EjvEKk4]{红龙面具 Red Dragon Mask}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.JADPCwRa7Wqe02Nf]{白龙面具 White Dragon Mask}</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"RoT","quantity":1,"weight":null,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"artifact","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"clothing","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":0,"stealth":false,"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZTn5n5VO8sqaer1W","name":"蜜酒 Tej","type":"consumable","img":"icons/consumables/drinks/alcohol-beer-stein-wooden-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>蜜酒是一种由蜂蜜制成的琥珀色发酵饮料。它比啤酒或麦酒更常见，也更受欢迎。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>一杯蜜酒在南扎路港卖 4 cp，在贝路利安堡卖 6 cp。</li>\n<li>一桶蜜酒容量为 1 加仑，在南扎路港卖 2 sp，在贝路利安堡卖 3 sp。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>蜜酒的销售由贸易亲王克薇欧泽垄断。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":5,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"autoDestroy":false},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"food"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZWzEz0wl51uG8tSX","name":"防护法杖 Staff of Defense","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/wands/wand-gem-purple.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这把法细长的空心法杖由玻璃制成但却有如橡木一样坚韧。其总重 3 磅。你必须与之同调才能获得其增益和施展其内的法术。</p>\n<p>持用该法杖时，你的护甲等级获得+1 加值。</p>\n<p>法杖有 10 发充能。持握法杖时，你可以用一个动作并消耗 1 发或更多充能以施展以下法术之一(该法术必须在你的职业法术列表内)：@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.KSMVJWpOg82yVTWG]{法师护甲 Mage Armor}(1 充能)或@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.6EjLIIN4ug7eSp4P]{护盾术 Shield}(2 充能)。这些法术无需任何构材。</p>\n<p>法杖每天黎明时恢复 [[/r 1d6 + 4]]发已消耗的充能。当充能耗 尽时，骰一次[[/r d20]]。如果骰值为 1，则法杖将被摧毁并化为一 滩水。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LMoP","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":10,"max":"10","per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6+@mod","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":"1d8+@mod"},"formula":"1d6+4","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"quarterstaff","properties":{"ver":true,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":true,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[{"label":"AC + 1","icon":"icons/weapons/wands/wand-gem-purple.webp","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.ac.bonus","mode":2,"value":"1"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"tint":null,"transfer":true,"flags":{},"_id":"51hlv1s6g06t86m6"}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":