{"_id":"iheXaRN4Riok3lFR","name":"盲视匕首 Dagger of Blindsight","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-crooked-black.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>这把匕首的边缘呈锯齿状，在它的柄端嵌有 一颗黑珍珠。与之同调的生物将获得 30 尺盲视。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WDMM","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"dex","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4+@mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"dagger","properties":{"fin":true,"lgt":true,"thr":true,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":true,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[{"_id":"xWdIVNli9ctGUEmt","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.senses.blindsight","mode":2,"value":"30"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-crooked-black.webp","label":"+30 ft. 盲视","origin":"Item.iheXaRN4Riok3lFR","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jO2WraOEGtW493o9","name":"甘提亚斯法杖 Gulthias Staff","type":"weapon","img":"icons/commodities/wood/kindling-stick-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>法杖（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>甘提亚斯法杖 由一棵甘提亚斯树的枝条制成，（见《怪物图鉴》中的枯枝怪blights 条目），法杖是一段多孔的黑色木头。其邪恶气息会让 30 尺内的野兽明显不适。法杖有 10 发充能，每天黄昏恢复[[/r 1d6+4]]发已经被消耗的充能。</p>\n<p>如果法杖被破坏或烧成灰烬，其木材会发出一声可怕而非人的尖叫，在 300 尺范围内都能听到，听到尖叫的枯萎怪会立刻枯萎死去。</p>\n<p><strong>吸血打击Vampiric Strike</strong>。该柄法杖可以被当作一柄有魔法的长棍来使用。若命中，其伤害等同于普通的长棍，你可以花费 1 点充能，恢复等于该武器造成伤害量的生命值。每花费一发充能，法杖的孔洞中都会渗出鲜红的血液，你必须成功通过一个DC 12 的感知豁免，否则将陷入短暂性疯狂（见《城主指南》第 8 章的“疯狂”）。</p>\n<p><strong>枯枝祸根Blight Bane</strong>。当你与法杖取得同调，枯枝怪及其他邪恶的植物角色将不视你为敌对状态，除非你伤害它们。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CoS","quantity":1,"weight":4,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":10,"max":"10","per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6 + @mod","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":"1d8 + @mod"},"formula":"1d6+4","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":12,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":true,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"mgc":true,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jUeOxHCvYLLAxCKC","name":"压缩空气 Bottled Breath","type":"consumable","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-corked-empty.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>这个瓶子里存有一股来自风元素的气流。</em></p>\n<p>当你吸气时，你可以选择呼出它，或者屏住它。如果你选择呼气，你得到@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.cGIrpk6h4Rf8QKV6]{造风术 Gust of Wind}的效果。如果你选择屏住呼吸，你不需要呼吸至多1个小时，你可以提前结束这个好处（例如，开口说话）。提前结束并不会给你带来呼气的好处。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PotA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"potion"},"effects":[{"_id":"lztI7OHOOA4O34gq","changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"rounds":1,"startTime":null,"seconds":3600},"icon":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-corked-empty.webp","label":"无需呼吸","origin":"Item.jUeOxHCvYLLAxCKC","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jdPiL569zynNNyFm","name":"蜘蛛法杖 Spider Staff","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/staves/staff-spiked.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n</div>\n<p>这把骇人的黑色法杖其顶端是一只蜘蛛的造型。该法杖重 6 磅。你必须与之同调才能获得其增益和施展其内的法术。</p>\n<p>该法杖可以作为一把长棍持用。用其作武器攻击命中时， 它可以额外造成[[/r 1d6]]的毒素伤害。</p>\n<p>法杖有 10 发充能。持握法杖时，你可以用一个动作并消 耗 1 发或更多充能以施展以下法术之一(该法术必须在你的 职业法术列表内)：@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.FNDS75JLYFQy4WUq]{蛛行术 Spider Climb}(1 充能)或@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.oopuSIBsaXzQKw1Q]{蛛网术 Web} (2 充能，法术豁免 DC 15)。这些法术无需任何构材。</p>\n<p>法杖每天黄昏时恢复[[/r 1d6 + 4]]发已消耗的充能。当充能耗 尽时，骰一次[[/r d20]]。如果骰值为 1，则法杖被摧毁并化为尘埃。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LMoP","quantity":1,"weight":6,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":10,"max":"10","per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6+@mod","bludgeoning"],["1d6","poison"]],"versatile":"1d8+@mod"},"formula":"1d6 + 4","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleM","baseItem":"quarterstaff","properties":{"ver":true,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":true,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jxURmyF1DjGly313","name":"丰盛之锅 Cauldron of Plenty","type":"equipment","img":"icons/consumables/drinks/coconut-fruit-milk.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>丰盛之锅是一口粗铜制的大锅，随着时间流逝，它表面的铜质已经变成绿色。它宽4尺，重50磅，锅口直径3.5尺，最多能装下30加仑的液体。它鼓起的侧面上刻着浮雕，图样为手持长勺、正在歇息的半羊人与宁芙们。这口大锅附有盖子与把手，下面还有五个防止倾斜的带爪支足。</p>\n<p>如果把水倒进锅里并搅拌1分钟，水就会变成一锅又热又丰盛的炖菜。每加仑水可为四个人提供一顿滋补餐。这些炖菜在锅里时将保持热度，取出后则会自然冷却。尽管炖菜很烫，但锅的外表仍然可以被安全地触碰。</p>\n<p>这口大锅可以制造三次炖菜，次数消耗完毕后它将停止工作。第二天的黎明时，它恢复所有可用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"IDRotF","quantity":1,"weight":50,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"minute","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"3","per":"day"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kF8cg1GLl3W4sTGS","name":"索敌飞镖 Seeker Dart","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/dagger-ringed-engraved-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这款小飞镖饰有像风一样的螺旋纹路，横跨整个镖柄。</p>\n<p>当你低声说出”搜索“并投掷这个飞镖时，它会在距离你120尺内的范围寻找你所选择的目标。你必须曾经见过该目标，但你在当下并不需要看到它。若目标不在射程内，或者你与它之间没有可通行的路径，飞镖将会掉落在地，且它的魔法也将消耗殆尽。否则的话，气元素之力将会立即引导飞镖穿过空中，直达目标。飞镖可以穿过1寸宽的开口，并且可以改变飞行方向来绕过转角。</p>\n<p>当飞镖抵达目标时，目标必须成功通过一次DC 16的敏捷豁免，否则将受到[[/r 1d4]]点穿刺伤害和[[/r 3d4]]点闪电伤害。在这之后，飞镖上的魔法将被消耗，变成一个普通的飞镖。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PotA","quantity":1,"weight":0.25,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"低声说出”搜索“。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4","piercing"],["3d4","lightning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":16,"scaling":"flat"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleR","baseItem":"dart","properties":{"rch":false,"amm":false,"ver":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":true,"mgc":true,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":true,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kVBrWTtfJr1gieBm","name":"玛塔洛托克 Matalotok","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/hammers/hammer-mallet-black.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>（需同调）</em></p>\n<p>冰霜之父玛塔洛托克是由霜巨人之神索列姆 Thrym制造的一把古老的锤子。玛塔洛托克是恶魔领主科斯彻奇 Kostchtchie最喜欢的武器，这把锤子触感寒冷刺骨，并被迷雾笼罩。</p>\n<p>握着玛塔洛托克时，你对冷冻伤害免疫。每当使用这把锤子对生物造成伤害时，锤子就会在30尺半径的范围内制造出强烈的寒流。该区域内的每个生物都会受到10([[/r 3d6]])点冷冻伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":2,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+@mod","bludgeoning"]],"versatile":"1d10+@mod"},"formula":"3d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"warhammer","properties":{"ver":true,"mgc":true,"rch":false,"amm":false,"ret":false,"fir":false,"ada":false,"fin":false,"lgt":false,"two":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"sil":false,"hvy":false,"rel":false,"foc":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":true,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"effects":[{"_id":"Amw5Li0KXDHA3o8Z","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.di.value","mode":2,"value":"cold"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/weapons/hammers/hammer-mallet-black.webp","label":"+ 冷冻免疫","origin":"Item.kVBrWTtfJr1gieBm","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kYFmdufc0Ni48jFE","name":"地狱火飞镖 Hellfire Dart","type":"weapon","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/weapons/dart.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种武器由炼狱铁铸造而成，并且具有地狱之火的纹路，能够在5尺范围内发出微光照明。</p>\n<p>任何被该武器杀死的类人生物的灵魂都会被注入冥河，在那里，他们立刻会重生为劣魔。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"BGDIA","quantity":1,"weight":0.25,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleR","baseItem":"dart","properties":{"fin":true,"thr":true,"amm":false,"hvy":false,"fir":false,"foc":false,"lgt":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"spc":false,"two":false,"ver":false,"ada":false,"mgc":true,"sil":false,"lod":false},"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kYZfnwIgnRwqnjTx","name":"如意箱 Abracadabrus","type":"equipment","img":"icons/containers/chest/chest-reinforced-steel-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>如意箱是一个装饰豪华且镶嵌有宝石的木质箱子，空无一物时重25磅。其内部空间约是一个边长1.5尺的立方体。</p>\n<p>该箱子共有20发充能。一个生物可以以一个动作触摸它紧闭着的盖子并消耗1发充能，同时宣言总价值不超过1gp的一个或多个非魔法物件（包括原料、食物以及液体）的名字。若被宣言的物件能被放置在箱子里，则它们魔法般地出现在其中（且其中没有其他物品）。例如，它可以变出一盘草莓、一碗肉汤、一壶水、一件动物标本或是一袋@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.81C7C7D9F004F3BB]{铁蒺藜 Caltrops}（20个）。该箱子变出的食物和饮料十分美味，但若在24小时后仍未被食用就会腐败变质，它创造的宝石以及贵金属则会在一分钟后消失。</p>\n<p>该箱子在每天黎明时会恢复[[/r 1d20]]发已消耗的充能次数。若你耗尽它的最后一发充能，骰一次[[/r d20]]。骰值为1时，它失去它的魔法（变成一个普通箱子），且镶嵌于其上的宝石将化为尘土。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"IDRotF","quantity":1,"weight":25,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":20,"max":"20","per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d20","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
