{"_id":"zciRnY2LdiPvPrxW","name":"和谐天平 Balance of Harmony","type":"equipment","img":"icons/tools/hand/scale-balances-merchant-brown.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>奇物</em></p>\n<p>这件天平的两个秤盘上分别纹有一个天界徽记和一个邪魔徽记。你可以用它主持施展@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.zeN5fxXLn4QE2YDa]{侦测善恶 Detect Evil and Good} 的法术仪式。以该方式使用时，你要先将其置放于稳定平面上，然后在两侧秤盘中倒入圣水，或是各放一枚价值100 gp 的透明宝石。若它保持静止则代表什么都没侦测到，若向善（天界徽记）或恶（邪魔徽记）的一侧倾斜并轻微摇摆则代表侦测出满足该法术作用条件，但既不属于善良也不属于邪恶阵营的生物。在仪式结束时触碰天平，你将知晓通常情况下相应法术所传达的讯息，随后效应终止。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TftYP","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":"","speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":false,"attuned":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
